(2, 1, '2014-08-05 19:43:42', '2014-08-05 19:43:42', '<h2>Scottsdale Senior Living</h2>\r\n<h3>Welcome to world-class service. Welcome to comfortable, elegant surroundings. Welcome to senior living in Scottsdale, WESTliving style.</h3>\r\nLooking for perfect weather in beautiful surroundings at a welcoming community with exceptional service? You''re right where you belong: McDowell Village in Scottsdale, Arizona.\r\n\r\nHere at McDowell Village, we''re dedicated to offering a true sense of belonging to seniors and their families. It''s a feeling you''ll notice the moment you''re invited to "make yourself at home" and continues through every thoughtful, personal detail.\r\n\r\nAs part of the WESTliving family, we understand the importance of world-class service. In fact, we even have a name for it: WESTclass service. We hire carefully and train extensively. The result? Team Members who are empowered to make a meaningful difference in the lives of those we serve and inspired to anticipate your next need – before you even know you have a next need.\r\n\r\nFrom physical and intellectual well-being to emotional and spiritual health, we take the time to know you as a person. Maybe your passion is fitness. May we suggest afternoon tai chi? Or perhaps you''d prefer to relax at our in-house spa or share a quiet desert sunset with a friend.\r\n\r\nYour warm, welcoming place to call home awaits at our Scottsdale senior living community. Call the number above or <a href="http://www.mcdowellvillage.com/leads/email_us/index.php">email us</a> to set up a tour and experience our difference in person.\r\n\r\n[ssba_hide]', 'McDowell Village', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'westliving-home-page', '', '', '2014-12-04 17:52:09', '2014-12-04 17:52:09', '', 0, 'http://new.westliving.net/?page_id=2', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(717, 8, '2014-11-19 19:20:42', '2014-11-19 19:20:42', '<h2>Scottsdale Senior Living</h2>\r\n<h3>Welcome to world-class service. Welcome to comfortable, elegant surroundings. Welcome to senior living, WESTliving style.</h3>\r\nLooking for perfect weather in beautiful surroundings at a welcoming community with exceptional service? You''re right where you belong: McDowell Village in Scottsdale, Arizona.\r\n\r\nHere at McDowell Village, we''re dedicated to offering a true sense of belonging to seniors and their families. It''s a feeling you''ll notice the moment you''re invited to "make yourself at home" and continues through every thoughtful, personal detail.\r\n\r\nAs part of the WESTliving family, we understand the importance of world-class service. In fact, we even have a name for it: WESTclass service. We hire carefully and train extensively. The result? Team Members who are empowered to make a meaningful difference in the lives of those we serve and inspired to anticipate your next need – before you even know you have a next need.\r\n\r\nFrom physical and intellectual well-being to emotional and spiritual health, we take the time to know you as a person. Maybe your passion is fitness. May we suggest afternoon tai chi? Or perhaps you''d prefer to relax at our in-house spa or share a quiet desert sunset with a friend.\r\n\r\nYour warm, welcoming place to call home awaits at our Scottsdale senior living community. Call the number above or <a href="http://www.mcdowellvillage.com/leads/email_us/index.php">email us</a> to set up a tour and experience our difference in person.\r\n\r\n[ssba_hide]', 'McDowell Village', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-11-19 19:20:42', '2014-11-19 19:20:42', '', 2, 'http://dev.mcdowellvillage.com/2-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(7, 1, '2014-08-07 16:09:00', '2014-08-07 16:09:00', '<h1>Welcome To Senior Living,<br>\r\nWESTliving Style.</h1>\r\n<h4>Senior Living with one goal in mind: to create a sense of belonging for seniors and their families.</h4>\r\n<p>Formed in early 2009, WESTliving offers a true sense of belonging for seniors and their families. It''s a feeling that begins the moment you''re invited to "make yourself at home," and continues through every thoughtful, personal detail. Because not only do we understand the importance of world-class customer service, we thrive on it. That''s why every Team Member is empowered and trained to anticipate needs and create solutions on the spot with one goal in mind: to surprise and delight every day. By combining our signature WESTclass service with comfortable, elegant surroundings, we''ve created a welcoming environment filled with empathy and respect.</p>', 'Home Page', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-08-07 16:09:00', '2014-08-07 16:09:00', '', 2, 'http://new.westliving.net/2-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(456, 7, '2014-10-02 22:20:35', '2014-10-02 22:20:35', '<h3>Senior care with a difference: a true sense of belonging.</h3>\r\nBalance is key for a Caregiver: you must replenish your own energy to be strong for those who depend on you day in and day out. Let us care for your family member in a safe, welcoming environment. Rest easy knowing that specially-trained Team Members will surround your loved one with care and respect.\r\n\r\nStay strong. Take care of yourself. Go out to lunch with friends. Shopping for the day. Or take that much-needed vacation. The Estancia Del Sol respite care program is available for an convenient overnight stay or for an extended respite stay. For fees and additional information, please contact us.  We''d welcome a chance to provide our services so you can take care of yourself.', 'Respite Care', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '264-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-10-02 22:20:35', '2014-10-02 22:20:35', '', 264, 'http://www.estanciads.com/redesign/264-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
