(12, 1, '2014-08-07 20:15:32', '2014-08-07 20:15:32', '<h3>Your go-to guide for all of our goings-on.</h3>\r\nQuick. Before you read any further, bookmark this page. Because this is your go-to guide for all things McDowell Village. Here, you''ll find the most up-to-date information on in-house activities, outings, special events and other daily programming for residents of our community.\r\n\r\nActivities include everything from shopping excursions and museum trips to yoga and aquatics classes to movie nights and ice cream socials. Check back soon to see what exciting new adventures we''ve added.\r\n\r\n<strong>Proud Winner of the 2012 Sterling Awards - Small Business</strong>\r\n\r\nMcDowell Village has been named the winner of the 26th annual Sterling Awards. Conducted by the Scottsdale Area Chamber of Commerce, this marquee event celebrates business excellence in our greater Scottsdale Valley community. One of the most coveted business awards in the area, the Sterling Awards judging committee selected McDowell Village as the winner over 30 other prestigious competitors after a rigorous application, judging and selection process.', 'About Us', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'about-us', '', '', '2014-11-25 23:24:27', '2014-11-25 23:24:27', '', 0, 'http://new.westliving.net/?page_id=12', 2, 'page', '', 0),
