(28, 1, '2014-08-07 20:18:58', '2014-08-07 20:18:58', '<h3>Step outside and make yourself at home.</h3>\r\nAt nearby Granite Reef Senior Center, you''ll have access to daily recreational classes and social services, combined with special events like talent shows – all just a stroll away through the garden path.\r\n\r\nPlus, it''s a quick 10-minute drive from the bustling downtown arts scene and destination shopping of historic Old Town, and only 13 miles from Phoenix. What could be more beautiful than that? The sunny weather here in Arizona of course. Let the sunshine begin.\r\n\r\n<strong>McDowell Village Area Attractions</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong><a href="http://www.scottsdaledowntown.com/SearchResults.aspx?findWord=old%20town" target="_blank">Old Town\r\n</a></strong>Downtown Scottsdale\r\nScottsdale, AZ 85251\r\n\r\n<strong><a href="http://www.scottsdaleperformingarts.org/index.php" target="_blank">Scottsdale Civic Center and Amphitheater\r\n</a></strong>7380 E. 2nd Street\r\nScottsdale, AZ 85251\r\n<strong>Phone</strong>: 480-994-ARTS (2787)\r\n\r\n<strong><a href="http://www.dbg.org/" target="_blank">Desert Botanical Gardens\r\n</a></strong>1201 N. Galvin Parkway\r\nPhoenix, AZ 85008\r\n<h4>McDowell Village Neighborhood Map</h4>\r\n<a href="http://www.mcdowellvillage.com/assets/images/senior-living-area-map.jpg"><img src="http://www.mcdowellvillage.com/assets/images/senior-living-area-map-thumb.jpg" alt="McDowell Village neighborhood map" /></a>', 'Local Attractions', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'local-attractions', '', '', '2014-11-25 23:30:00', '2014-11-25 23:30:00', '', 12, 'http://new.westliving.net/?page_id=28', 5, 'page', '', 0),
(359, 2, '2014-09-11 17:37:17', '2014-09-11 17:37:17', '<h3>Step outside and make yourself at home.</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Located just south of California''s state capital, Elk Grove is home of the official California weigh-off site for a national Giant Pumpkin contest, and a host of other activities. Dine at one of the area''s tasty restaurants, pick your favorite of the city''s 50 parks for a stroll, or shop at one of the charming small shops in Old Town Elk Grove.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Festivals abound here, including the popular Elk Grove Western Festival.  What could be more beautiful than that? The sunny weather here in Elk Grove of course. Let the sunshine and activities begin.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>The Commons at Elk Grove Area Attractions:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>Laguna Creek Parkway</li>\r\n    <li>Stone Lake Refuge</li>\r\n    <li>Over 70 restaurants</li>\r\n    <li>Sports events and golf courses</li>\r\n    <li>Farmers markets</li>\r\n    <li>Seasonal festivals</li>\r\n    <li>Cosumnes River Preserve</li>\r\n    <li>Approximately 26 miles from the Sacramento International Airport</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Local Attractions', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '28-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-09-11 17:37:17', '2014-09-11 17:37:17', '', 28, 'http://www.estanciads.com/redesign/28-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
