(67, 1, '2014-08-07 23:43:04', '2014-08-07 23:43:04', '<p class="intro-text">Senior living communities with a difference: a true sense of belonging</p>\r\n<h3>ARIZONA</h3>\r\n<h4><a href="http://www.mcdowellvillage.com/" target="_blank">McDowell Village</a></h4>\r\n<p>McDowell Village is a 207 unit independent and assisted living community located in South Scottsdale - &frac14; mile west of highway 101 and 2 miles east of highway 202, which provides access to downtown Phoenix. The Community benefits from the City of Scottsdale sponsored 38,000 square foot Granite Reef Senior Center, which provides educational, recreational and social activities.&nbsp;<a href="http://www.mcdowellvillage.com/" target="_blank">MORE &gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3>CALIFORNIA</h3>\r\n<h4><a href="http://www.commonsatelkgrove.com/" target="_blank">The Commons at Elk Grove</a></h4>\r\n<p>The Commons at Elk Grove is a 95 unit independent, assisted living and memory care community conveniently located in the heart of Elk Grove. Residents enjoy private, spacious studios, one-and two-bedroom suites surrounded by their own furniture and personal treasures. Residents have a place to call their own. Cozy yet elegant surroundings, stimulating activities and excursions, exceptional amenities and extra help when needed-you''ll find all this and more at The Commons at Elk Grove Assisted Living Community. <a href="http://www.commonsatelkgrove.com/" target="_blank">MORE &gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n\r\n<h4><a href="http://www.commonsonthornton.com" target="_blank">The Commons on Thornton</a></h4>\r\n<p>The Commons on Thornton is a 100 unit independent, assisted living and memory care community conveniently located in the heart of the Central Valley. Residents enjoy private, spacious studios, one-and two-bedroom suites surrounded by their own furniture and personal treasures. Residents have a place to call their own. Cozy yet elegant surroundings, stimulating activities and excursions, exceptional amenities and extra help when needed-you''ll find all this and more at The Commons&nbsp;on Thornton&nbsp;Assisted Living Community. <a href="http://www.commonsonthornton.com" target="_blank">MORE &gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n\r\n<h4><a href="http://www.commonsatunionranch.com" target="_blank">The Commons at Union Ranch</a></h4>\r\n<p>The Commons at Union Ranch is a 98 unit independent, assisted living and memory care community conveniently located in the heart of the Central Valley. Residents enjoy private, spacious studios, one-and two-bedroom suites surrounded by their own furniture and personal treasures. Residents have a place to call their own. Cozy yet elegant surroundings, stimulating activities and excursions, exceptional amenities and extra help when needed-you''ll find all this and more at The Commons at Union Ranch Assisted Living Community. <a href="http://www.commonsatunionranch.com" target="_blank">MORE &gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n\r\n<h4><a href="http://www.dalecommons.com" target="_blank">Dale Commons</a></h4>\r\n<p>Dale Commons is a 98 unit independent and assisted living community located in the heart of Stanislaus County, Modesto. Residents enjoy private, spacious studios, one-and two-bedroom suites surrounded by their own furniture and personal treasures. Residents have a place to call their own. Cozy yet elegant surroundings, stimulating activities and excursions, exceptional amenities and extra help when needed-you''ll find all this and more at Dale Commons Assisted Living Community. <a href="http://www.dalecommons.com" target="_blank">MORE &gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n\r\n<h4><a href="http://www.estanciads.com">Estancia Del Sol</a></h4>\r\n<p><strong></strong></p>\r\n<p>Estancia Del Sol is a 117 unit independent, assisted living and memory care community conveniently located in the heart of Corona, CA. Residents enjoy private, spacious studios, one-and two-bedroom suites surrounded by their own furniture and personal treasures. Residents have a place to call their own. Cozy yet elegant surroundings, stimulating activities and excursions, exceptional amenities and extra help when needed-you''ll find all this and more at Estancia Del Sol Assisted Living Community. <a href="http://www.estanciads.com">MORE &gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n\r\n<h4><a href="http://www.thereserveatthousandoaks.com" target="_blank">The Reserve at Thousand Oaks</a></h4>\r\n<p>The Reserve at Thousand Oaks is a 140 unit independent and assisted living community occupying a magnificent hilltop site in Thousand Oaks, affording breathtaking views of the entire Conejos Valley and the Santa Rosa foothills. The Ventura freeway is less than 10 minutes from your door and the Pacific Ocean is only 30 minutes to the south through the beautiful Santa Monica Mountains. <a href="http://www.thereserveatthousandoaks.com" target="_blank">MORE &gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3>WASHINGTON</h3>\r\n<h4><a href="http://www.thebellettini.com" target="_blank">The Bellettini</a></h4>\r\n<p>The Bellettini offers 145 senior apartment homes for those over the age of 62, featuring 25 different floor plans only steps away from the energy and buzz of downtown Bellevue, within the calm and comfort of residential living. One- and two-bedroom apartments range from 700 square feet to 2,400 square feet. Assisted living services can be added and customized at any time. <a href="http://www.thebellettini.com" target="_blank">MORE &gt;&gt;</a></p>', 'Locations', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '10-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-08-07 23:43:04', '2014-08-07 23:43:04', '', 10, 'http://new.westliving.net/10-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(66, 1, '2014-08-07 23:33:19', '2014-08-07 23:33:19', '<p class="intro-text">Senior living communities with a difference: a true sense of belonging</p>\r\n<h3>ARIZONA</h3>\r\n<h4><a href="http://mcdowellvillage.com.s84794.gridserver.com" target="_blank">McDowell Village</a></h4>\r\n<p>McDowell Village is a 207 unit independent and assisted living community located in South Scottsdale - &frac14; mile west of highway 101 and 2 miles east of highway 202, which provides access to downtown Phoenix. The Community benefits from the City of Scottsdale sponsored 38,000 square foot Granite Reef Senior Center, which provides educational, recreational and social activities.&nbsp;<a href="http://mcdowellvillage.com.s84794.gridserver.com" target="_blank">MORE &gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3>CALIFORNIA</h3>\r\n<h4><a href="http://commonsatelkgrove.com.s84794.gridserver.com" target="_blank">The Commons at Elk Grove</a></h4>\r\n<p>The Commons at Elk Grove is a 95 unit independent, assisted living and memory care community conveniently located in the heart of Elk Grove. Residents enjoy private, spacious studios, one-and two-bedroom suites surrounded by their own furniture and personal treasures. Residents have a place to call their own. Cozy yet elegant surroundings, stimulating activities and excursions, exceptional amenities and extra help when needed-you''ll find all this and more at The Commons at Elk Grove Assisted Living Community. <a href="http://commonsatelkgrove.com.s84794.gridserver.com" target="_blank">MORE &gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n\r\n<h4><a href="http://commonsonthornton.com.s84794.gridserver.com" target="_blank">The Commons on Thornton</a></h4>\r\n<p>The Commons on Thornton is a 100 unit independent, assisted living and memory care community conveniently located in the heart of the Central Valley. Residents enjoy private, spacious studios, one-and two-bedroom suites surrounded by their own furniture and personal treasures. Residents have a place to call their own. Cozy yet elegant surroundings, stimulating activities and excursions, exceptional amenities and extra help when needed-you''ll find all this and more at The Commons&nbsp;on Thornton&nbsp;Assisted Living Community. <a href="http://commonsonthornton.com.s84794.gridserver.com" target="_blank">MORE &gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n\r\n<h4><a href="http://commonsatunionranch.com.s84794.gridserver.com" target="_blank">The Commons at Union Ranch</a></h4>\r\n<p>The Commons at Union Ranch is a 98 unit independent, assisted living and memory care community conveniently located in the heart of the Central Valley. Residents enjoy private, spacious studios, one-and two-bedroom suites surrounded by their own furniture and personal treasures. Residents have a place to call their own. Cozy yet elegant surroundings, stimulating activities and excursions, exceptional amenities and extra help when needed-you''ll find all this and more at The Commons at Union Ranch Assisted Living Community. <a href="http://commonsatunionranch.com.s84794.gridserver.com" target="_blank">MORE &gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n\r\n<h4><a href="http://dalecommons.com.s84794.gridserver.com" target="_blank">Dale Commons</a></h4>\r\n<p>Dale Commons is a 98 unit independent and assisted living community located in the heart of Stanislaus County, Modesto. Residents enjoy private, spacious studios, one-and two-bedroom suites surrounded by their own furniture and personal treasures. Residents have a place to call their own. Cozy yet elegant surroundings, stimulating activities and excursions, exceptional amenities and extra help when needed-you''ll find all this and more at Dale Commons Assisted Living Community. <a href="http://dalecommons.com.s84794.gridserver.com" target="_blank">MORE &gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n\r\n<h4><a href="http://doscolinasliving.com.s84794.gridserver.com" target="_blank">Dos Colinas</a> <em>(coming soon)</em></h4>\r\n<p>Dos Colinas is a planned 309 unit Continuing Care Retirement Community in Carlsbad, California. The sprawling campus features multi-levels of independent, assisted and memory care services for residents at all stages of life. Dos Colinas features everything from quaint studios to 1,500 square feet apartments to even larger private cottages for those who want the home away from home. <a href="http://doscolinasliving.com.s84794.gridserver.com" target="_blank">MORE &gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n\r\n<h4><a href="http://thereserveatthousandoaks.com.s84794.gridserver.com" target="_blank">The Reserve at Thousand Oaks</a></h4>\r\n<p>The Reserve at Thousand Oaks is a 140 unit independent and assisted living community occupying a magnificent hilltop site in Thousand Oaks, affording breathtaking views of the entire Conejos Valley and the Santa Rosa foothills. The Ventura freeway is less than 10 minutes from your door and the Pacific Ocean is only 30 minutes to the south through the beautiful Santa Monica Mountains. <a href="http://thereserveatthousandoaks.com.s84794.gridserver.com" target="_blank">MORE &gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3>WASHINGTON</h3>\r\n<h4><a href="http://www.thebellettini.com" target="_blank">The Bellettini</a></h4>\r\n<p>The Bellettini offers 145 senior apartment homes for those over the age of 62, featuring 25 different floor plans only steps away from the energy and buzz of downtown Bellevue, within the calm and comfort of residential living. One- and two-bedroom apartments range from 700 square feet to 2,400 square feet. Assisted living services can be added and customized at any time. <a href="http://www.thebellettini.com" target="_blank">MORE &gt;&gt;</a></p>', 'Locations', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '10-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-08-07 23:33:19', '2014-08-07 23:33:19', '', 10, 'http://new.westliving.net/10-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
