(72, 1, '2014-08-08 17:02:15', '2014-08-08 17:02:15', '<p>At WESTliving our mission centers on delivering exceptional services and experiences by inspiring and empowering our Team Members to make a meaningful difference in the lives of those we serve.  WESTliving’s culture is grounded in the fact that these daily actions and behaviors support our shared vision to be the most respected and recognized service company in the world.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>WESTliving was formed in early 2009 to own and operate hospitality based senior living communities providing exceptional variety of lifestyles, wellness, and care options. WESTclass uncompromising quality is apparent with respect to building standards, amenities, Team Member’s commitment, as well as the integration of innovative programs and wellness options designed to accommodate and support an array of lifestyles and needs.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The WESTclass Team of talented and experienced leaders in the industry bring a customer centered approach to senior living. Team members are driven by WESTliving Core Values, Mission, and Service Standards as guiding principles to be engaged, responsible and attentive to all we serve in achieving our Vision.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>WESTliving is located in Carlsbad, California and operates within the Pacific and Southwest regions of the United States. Maintaining a boutique and uniquely focused approached as a regional operator enables WESTliving to stay true to its vision of service excellence.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>At WESTliving, we make it easy for residents to remain a part of the larger community just outside their door. This is why we reach out into the neighborhood to support and partner with cultural centers, schools and senior advocacy groups, to name a few. You will find intergenerational experiences, philanthropy and good ol’ neighborliness alive and well. This is what we call a true sense of belonging.</p>', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '12-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-08-08 17:02:15', '2014-08-08 17:02:15', '', 12, 'http://new.westliving.net/12-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(73, 1, '2014-08-08 17:05:24', '2014-08-08 17:05:24', '<p>At WESTliving, creating a customer experience and anticipating needs through our WESTclass service is our hallmark. Anyone can say ‘make yourself at home.’ It is only when the warm and friendly environment meets genuine hospitality that brings those words to life.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Whatever your lifestyle living needs or wishes are, each day we strive to provide our customers with a WESTclass experience. “WESTclass” is our word that expresses a world-class standard in hospitality and services for older adults. The foundational values, the WESTliving mission and vision are what we build upon in careful selection of our Team Members to creating the WESTclass experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Our Values</h3>\r\n<h4>I.N.S.P.I.R.E.</h4>\r\n<p><strong>Integrity</strong> - We say what we do and do what we say – we are accountable.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Neighborliness</strong> - We build lasting relationships in and around our communities.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Service</strong> - We deliver WESTclass service.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Profitability</strong> - We reinvest our financial success in our communities and our team members.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Innovation</strong> - We are forward-thinking and committed to continuous improvement.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Respect</strong> - We value diversity and encourage individual thinking.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Excellence</strong> - We focus on the details and provide a WESTclass experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Our Mission</h3>\r\n<p>With absolute devotion, WESTliving delivers exceptional service and experiences by inspiring and empowering our team members to make a meaningful difference in the lives of those we serve.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Our Vision</h3>\r\n<p>WESTliving will be the most respected and recognized service company in the world.</p>', 'Our Mission', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '20-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-08-08 17:05:24', '2014-08-08 17:05:24', '', 20, 'http://new.westliving.net/20-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
