(98, 1, '2014-08-08 18:45:38', '2014-08-08 18:45:38', '<p class="intro-text">WESTliving''s hospitality focused approach to senior living is, in part, rooted in the business successes of Gary &amp; Mary West and their philosophy of gauging one''s success by what we are able to accomplish for our customers. Within WESTliving, serving our customers means continuing to foster ideas and expand our own capabilities to meet the growing and diverse needs of our customers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Operating historically in an industry focused simply on trying to address the care needs of the elderly, WESTliving looks to shape senior housing and its own destiny by focusing on service excellence.&nbsp;Hiring, training, and mentoring service talented professionals, which brings our service culture to the benefit of others; leading to our success. WESTliving is among the first in its industry to adopt a set of Service Standards that parallel those of some of the best recognized services delivery companies in the world.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Today, we continue to bring added value to our own customer relationships and delivery platform, by bringing innovative ideas and improved possibilities to those we serve.&nbsp; We shamelessly take ideas and inspiration from other service-business leaders as well as other West businesses started by Gary and Mary that are more traditionally known for promoting hospitality and service quality.&nbsp; Our own restaurant and hotel businesses are operations with competencies and specialty areas that add to our base of knowledge and capabilities.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>West Inn &amp; Suites</strong>, an independent boutique hotel featuring 86 rooms with 36 suites opened its doors to in May of 2006. This pet-friendly hotel prides itself in superior guest service with value added amenities. Competing with brand properties in the local market makes unique services and amenities the hallmark for success. A complimentary breakfast buffet, free parking and Wi-Fi along with shuttle service within Carlsbad were the core value standards since opening. West Inn and Suites'' amenities include: Aveda products, a heated swimming pool (salt-water) and spa along with a business and fitness center. Our seasonal wine pour along with cookies and milk at bedtime make for a most enjoyable stay.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The second restaurant, <strong>Bistro West®</strong>, can be described as a chef driven bistro, serving contemporary comfort foods. It also features a diverse international wine list with an extensive selection of wines by the glass. Since it opened in May of 2007, the goal remains the same; we promise to provide our guests great food, wines and service in a beautiful restaurant.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The first restaurant in Cannon Court was an exciting fine dining steak house, <strong>West Steak Seafood &amp; Spirits®</strong>. The goal was to provide a fantastic dining experience by featuring only the finest foods, wine and service in a beautiful surrounding. This restaurant opened in December of 2005 to rave reviews and continues to build on its success. West Steak Seafood &amp; Spirits® specializes in prime steaks, but also has a large menu of appetizers, salads, seafood and homemade desserts.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Westmart®</strong> was the first building in Cannon Court and opened for business in January of 2004. This premier gas station has 16 gasoline and 8 diesel fueling points along with a convenience store. Priding itself on competitive pricing, clean facilities, and excellent customer service, Westmart® adds to the amenities available at Cannon Court.</p>', 'West Family of Companies', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '26-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-08-08 18:45:38', '2014-08-08 18:45:38', '', 26, 'http://new.westliving.net/26-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
