(455, 7, '2014-10-02 22:44:22', '2014-10-02 22:44:22', '<h2>Senior care service for the caregiver and their loved one!</h2>\nBalance is key for a caregiver!  Replenishing your own energy to remain strong for those who depend on you day in and day can''t be the last item on the <em>to do</em> list all the time. Let us care for your family member in our safe, welcoming environment. Rest easy knowing that specially-trained Team Members will surround your loved one with care and respect, while you get a chance to take care of yourself.\n\nYour loved one knows you are strong and always place their needs first. Our respite stay program will allow you to feel guilt-free to take some time for yourself. Go out to lunch with friends. Shopping for the day. Or take that much-needed vacation. The Estancia Del Sol respite care program is available for an convenient overnight stay or for an extended respite stay.\n\nFor fees and additional information, please contact us.  We''re at your service so you can take care of yourself.', 'Respite Care', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '264-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-10-02 22:44:22', '2014-10-02 22:44:22', '', 264, 'http://www.estanciads.com/redesign/264-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(454, 7, '2014-10-02 22:13:06', '2014-10-02 22:13:06', '<h3>A respectful, safe place to call home.</h3>\r\nAs part of the WESTliving family, Estancia Del Sol offers the Renaissance Memory Care program: a unique approach that blends years of Alzheimer''s and other related dementia care experience with contemporary research developed by leaders in the field.\r\n\r\nEvery Team Member throughout the community completes extensive training in the Renaissance Memory Care program.  This creates a team approach to services in a consistently safe, respectful, compassionate, and supportive environment.\r\n\r\nOur primary focus is to create a home-like environment that encourages resident engagement in activities that draw on individual interests.  We collaborate with family members in customizing a plan that meets individual needs and desires, to enrich the daily life of Alzheimer''s or dementia residents . This close partnership with family, friends, volunteers and community groups is integral to the well-being of each resident.\r\n\r\n<strong>Memory, Alzheimer''s &amp; Dementia Care Services Include:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>High Team Member to Resident Ratios</li>\r\n	<li>24 Hour Specially Trained Team Members on Duty</li>\r\n	<li>Medication Management</li>\r\n	<li>Assistance with Activities of Daily Living</li>\r\n	<li>Individualized Care Management Programs</li>\r\n	<li>Balanced, Nutritious Meals Approved by a Nutritionist</li>\r\n	<li>Alzheimer''s and Dementia Family Support and Involvement</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Memory Care', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '262-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-10-02 22:13:06', '2014-10-02 22:13:06', '', 262, 'http://www.estanciads.com/redesign/262-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(453, 7, '2014-10-02 22:12:28', '2014-10-02 22:12:28', '<h3>A respectful, safe place to call home.</h3>\nAs part of the WESTliving family, Estancia Del Sol offers the Renaissance Memory Care program: a unique approach that blends years of Alzheimer''s and other related dementia care experience with contemporary research developed by leaders in the field.\n\nEvery Team Member throughout the community completes extensive training in the Renaissance Memory Care program.  This creates a team approach to services in a consistently safe, respectful, compassionate, and supportive environment.\n\nOur primary focus is to create a home-like environment that encourages resident engagement in activities that draw on individual interests.  We collaborate with family members to enrich the daily life of Alzheimer''s or dementia residents in customizing a plan that meets individual needs and desires. This close partnership with family, friends, volunteers and community groups is integral to the well-being of each resident.\n\n<strong>Memory, Alzheimer''s &amp; Dementia Care Services Include:</strong>\n<ul>\n	<li>High Team Member to Resident Ratios</li>\n	<li>24 Hour Specially Trained Team Members on Duty</li>\n	<li>Medication Management</li>\n	<li>Assistance with Activities of Daily Living</li>\n	<li>Individualized Care Management Programs</li>\n	<li>Balanced, Nutritious Meals Approved by a Nutritionist</li>\n	<li>Alzheimer''s and Dementia Family Support and Involvement</li>\n</ul>', 'Memory Care', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '262-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-10-02 22:12:28', '2014-10-02 22:12:28', '', 262, 'http://www.estanciads.com/redesign/262-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(393, 2, '2014-09-22 22:22:10', '2014-09-22 22:22:10', '<p class="intro-text">Isn''t it time you spent time with people as interesting as you?</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Be yourself. This will now be different. You''re right where you belong.</h3>\r\nHe says tomato. She says tomahto. And that''s exactly what makes things interesting around here. By embracing everyone''s uniqueness, we''ve created a community where everyone feels like they belong. That''s why here at The Commons at Elk Grove, you can choose the lifestyle option that fits you. Choose from Elk Grove senior care options including independent living, living that offers assistance with your everyday routine, Alzheimer''s and dementia care or respite care. Plus our wide range of amenities and activities means there''s always something to inspire, excite, relax or intrigue. Why let another day go by without learning tai chi? Without taking up watercolors? Without strolling the garden? Don''t worry, we have the details covered. All you have to do is enjoy.', 'Living Options', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '10-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-09-22 22:22:10', '2014-09-22 22:22:10', '', 10, 'http://www.estanciads.com/redesign/10-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
