(633, 2, '2014-11-11 20:49:14', '2014-11-11 20:49:14', '<h3>Estancia Del Sol is opening soon in Corona. We’re hosting a JOB FAIR and we want to meet you!</h3>\r\nWe’re looking for people who not only understand the importance of world-class customer service, they actually thrive on it.\r\n<h3>Stop by on NOVEMBER 19th\r\n9am – 1pm • 3pm – 7pm</h3>\r\n<strong>BE</strong>come a WESTliving team member – it will enhance your life.\r\n\r\nCurrently Hiring:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Housekeepers</li>\r\n	<li>Maintenance Assistant</li>\r\n	<li>Drivers (must possess Class B license w/passenger endorsement)</li>\r\n	<li>Resident Attendants (personal care)</li>\r\n	<li>REN Manager (Memory Care)</li>\r\n	<li>Assisted Living Manager</li>\r\n	<li>Medication Attendants</li>\r\n	<li>Concierge</li>\r\n	<li>Cooks</li>\r\n	<li>Stewards (dishwasher)</li>\r\n	<li>Activity Manager</li>\r\n	<li>WESTfitness Instructor</li>\r\n	<li>Restaurant Servers</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nEOE, Competitive Wages, Full Benefit Package', 'Job Fair', 'Estancia Del Sol is opening soon in Corona. We’re hosting a JOB FAIR and we want to meet you!', 'trash', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'job-fair', '', '', '2014-11-19 16:55:34', '2014-11-19 16:55:34', '', 0, 'http://www.estanciads.com/?post_type=tribe_events&#038;p=633', 0, 'tribe_events', '', 0);
