(392, 2, '2014-09-16 17:34:02', '2014-09-16 17:34:02', '<h3>Welcome to senior living, WESTliving Style.</h3>\r\n\r\nFormed in early 2009, WESTliving offers a true sense of belonging for seniors and their families. It’s a feeling that begins the moment you’re invited to “make yourself at home” and continues through every thoughtful, personal detail. Because not only do we understand the importance of world-class customer service, we thrive on it. That’s why every Team Member is empowered and trained to anticipate needs and create solutions on the spot with one goal in mind: to surprise and delight every day. By combining our signature WESTclass service with comfortable, elegant surroundings, we’ve created a welcoming environment filled with empathy and respect.\r\n\r\nWESTliving is located in Carlsbad, California and owns and operates senior housing communities in California, Washington, and Arizona. There are additional communities under development in California.\r\n\r\nFor more about WESTliving, please visit: <a href="http://www.westliving.net/" target="_blank">www.westliving.net</a>.', 'About WESTliving', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '254-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-09-16 17:34:02', '2014-09-16 17:34:02', '', 254, 'http://www.estanciads.com/redesign/254-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(395, 2, '2014-09-22 22:24:27', '2014-09-22 22:24:27', '<p class="intro-text">Isn''t it time you spent time with people as interesting as you?</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Be yourself. You''re right where you belong.</h3>\r\nHe says tomato. She says tomahto. And that''s exactly what makes things interesting around here. By embracing everyone''s uniqueness, we''ve created a community where everyone feels like they belong. That''s why here at The Commons at Elk Grove, you can choose the lifestyle option that fits you. Choose from Elk Grove senior care options including independent living, living that offers assistance with your everyday routine, Alzheimer''s and dementia care or respite care. Plus our wide range of amenities and activities means there''s always something to inspire, excite, relax or intrigue. Why let another day go by without learning tai chi? Without taking up watercolors? Without strolling the garden? Don''t worry, we have the details covered. All you have to do is enjoy.', 'Senior Living Options', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '10-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-09-22 22:24:27', '2014-09-22 22:24:27', '', 10, 'http://www.estanciads.com/redesign/10-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
