(176, 1, '2014-06-24 23:48:29', '2014-06-24 23:48:29', '<h3>Location: Modesto CA and Stockton CA</h3>\r\n<h2>Position Summary:</h2>\r\nThe Maintenance Assistant will assist the Maintenance Director in ensuring that the building, equipment, and grounds are maintained in good order and that preventive measures are taken to extend the life and value of the community.\r\n\r\nWESTliving is looking to fill this position with a person who possesses the following talents:\r\n\r\n<strong>Achiever</strong> – Self-driven and motivated by achieving defined stated goals.\r\n<strong>Ethics</strong> – A clear understanding of right and wrong which guides your actions.\r\n<strong>Service</strong> – A drive to be of service to others.\r\n\r\nIn addition to the talents listed above WESTliving is looking to fill this position with a person who possesses the following:\r\n<h3>Skills</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Perform installation and repairs within area of expertise including mechanical, electrical, plumbing, carpentry and painting and perform installation and repairs according to code.</li>\r\n	<li>Strong verbal, written, and interpersonal communication skills.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Knowledge</h3>\r\n1 -3 years of building maintenance experience\r\n<h3>About us</h3>\r\nWESTliving was formed in early 2009 to own and operate hospitality based senior living communities. Our communities provide a variety of lifestyles, wellness, and care options. We are uncompromising in our commitment to quality and service excellence. WESTliving’s culture is grounded in the fact that daily actions and behaviors support our shared vision to be the most respected and recognized service company in the world.\r\n\r\nThe WESTclass Team of talented and experienced leaders in the industry bring a customer centered approach to senior living. Team members are driven by WESTliving Core Values, Mission, and Service Standards as guiding principles to be engaged, responsible and attentive to all we serve in achieving our Vision.\r\n<h3>Join our Team!</h3>\r\nAs we look forward to future growth, we are committed to providing our employees with the tools they need to succeed, as well as providing a challenging work environment with opportunities to make meaningful contributions. Our benefits package includes: medical, dental, vision, life insurance, vacation, and a 401(k) plan with a generous employer match.', 'Maintenance Assistant', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'maintenance-assistant-dale-thorton-commons', '', '', '2014-08-28 20:27:17', '2014-08-28 20:27:17', '', 0, 'http://new.westliving.net/?post_type=careers&#038;p=176', 0, 'careers', '', 0),
