(187, 2, '2014-08-15 17:18:30', '2014-08-15 17:18:30', '<h3>Location: Corona, CA</h3>\r\n<h2>Position Summary:</h2>\r\n\r\nWe are seeking an individual with senior living management experience to assume the role of Resident Services Director. The purpose of this position is to plan, organize, develop, and direct Resident Care Services in accordance with WESTliving’s best practices and regulatory standards through Person-Centered Care to assure the highest degree of customer service and satisfaction\r\n\r\nWESTliving is looking to fill this position with a person who possesses the following talents:\r\n\r\nDeveloper: A need to invest in others and to derive satisfaction in doing so\r\nService: A need to be of service to others\r\nIndividualized Perception: An awareness of and attentiveness to individual differences\r\nCreativity: An ability to break existing configurations in favor of more affective/appealing ones\r\nEmpathy: An ability to identify the feelings and perspectives of others\r\n\r\n\r\nIn addition to the talents listed above WESTliving is looking to fill this position with a person who possesses the following:\r\n\r\n<h3>Skills</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>Must be able to read written direction, comprehend verbal instruction, and write at a level necessary to accomplish the job</li>\r\n    <li>RCFE Administrator Certificate required (or willing to obtain)</li>\r\n    <li>Ability to supervise and train staff</li>\r\n    <li>Knowledge to conduct pre-admission assessments for prospective residents</li>	\r\n    <li>Experience conducting staff meetings</li>	\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>Knowledge</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>LVN or RN training and current license</li>\r\n    <li>2-4 years of experience in long term care</li>\r\n    <li>2 years of experience in supervisory role</li> \r\n    <li>Experience with memory care preferred</li>\r\n    <li>Familiar with Title 22 Regulations</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>About us</h3>\r\nWESTliving was formed in early 2009 to own and operate hospitality based senior living communities. Our communities provide a variety of lifestyles, wellness, and care options. We are uncompromising in our commitment to quality and service excellence. WESTliving’s culture is grounded in the fact that daily actions and behaviors support our shared vision to be the most respected and recognized service company in the world.\r\n\r\nThe WESTclass Team of talented and experienced leaders in the industry bring a customer centered approach to senior living. Team members are driven by WESTliving Core Values, Mission, and Service Standards as guiding principles to be engaged, responsible and attentive to all we serve in achieving our Vision.\r\n\r\n<h3>Join our Team!</h3>\r\nAs we look forward to future growth, we are committed to providing our employees with the tools they need to succeed, as well as providing a challenging work environment with opportunities to make meaningful contributions. Our benefits package includes: medical, dental, vision, life insurance, vacation, and a 401(k) plan with a generous employer match.', 'Resident Services Director', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '183-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-08-15 17:18:30', '2014-08-15 17:18:30', '', 183, 'http://new.westliving.net/183-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(188, 1, '2014-07-30 17:29:42', '2014-07-30 17:29:42', '<h3>Location: Corona, CA</h3>\r\n<h2>Position Summary:</h2>\r\n\r\nWe are seeking an individual with culinary or restaurant experience to assume the role of Food and Beverage Director for our hospitality based senior living community. This person will be responsible for managing and coordinating all the daily functions within the department as well as the staff members. This position includes monitoring the services of food and drinks, as well as knowledge of labor laws and health compliance regulations. \r\n\r\nWESTliving is looking to fill this position with a person who possesses the following talents:\r\n\r\n<strong>Service</strong> - A drive to be of service to others\r\n<strong>Discipline</strong> - A need to impose structure into life and work\r\n<strong>Individualized Perception</strong> - An awareness of and attentiveness to individual differences\r\n<strong>Developer</strong> - A need to invest in others and to derive satisfaction in doing so\r\n<strong>Command</strong> - An ability to take charge\r\n\r\nIn addition to the talents listed above WESTliving is looking to fill this position with a person who possesses the following:\r\n\r\n<h3>Skills</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>Able to instruct as well as listen. Effectively understands, deciphers and relates WESTliving’s vision to employees</li>\r\n    <li>Knowledge of principles and processes for providing customer and personal services. This includes customer needs assessment, meeting quality standards for services, and evaluation of customer satisfaction</li>\r\n    <li>Knowledge of principles and methods for curriculum and training design as well as the ability to teach and instruct individuals</li>\r\n    <li>Knowledge of raw materials, production processes, quality control, costs, and other techniques for maximizing effective manufacturing and distribution of goods</li>\r\n    <li>Ability to cook and prepare food in accordance with culinary program</li