(331, 2, '2014-09-10 19:20:31', '2014-09-10 19:20:31', '<h3>This is what senior living was meant to be.</h3>\r\n\r\nYou''ve worked hard. Now it''s time to reap the rewards. And what better place than in a sunny central California community filled with interesting neighbors, new friends and ever-attentive service?\r\n\r\nAt The Commons at Elk Grove, community spaces are more than extensions of your home, they''re extensions of your life. Here, you''ll find the inviting, the comfortable, even the extraordinary. Our gym will build your body and spirit with cardio and strength training, and improve your agility and focus with yoga or tai chi. After your workout, step outside and enjoy our landscaped grounds and walking path. Or just sit and soak up the sunshine.\r\n\r\nOur computer lounge makes it easy to download photos, email, catch up on Facebook, research your next exciting travel adventure or try out our brain fitness program. After a full day like this, be sure to pamper yourself with a haircut, manicure or pedicure in the salon.\r\n\r\nNext, imagine walking into the dining room and seeing your famous homemade spaghetti on the dinner menu. We didn''t read your mind, but you''ll feel like we did. Because we take the time to get to know you as a person. Small, meaningful touches are a way of life around here.\r\n\r\nYou could get used to independent living in Elk Grove like this.', 'Independent Living', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '258-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-09-10 19:20:31', '2014-09-10 19:20:31', '', 258, 'http://www.estanciads.com/redesign/258-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(332, 2, '2014-09-10 19:26:18', '2014-09-10 19:26:18', '<h3>Just because you need a little hand now and then doesn''t mean you can''t still lead.</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>At The Commons at Elk Grove, assisted living means person-centered care. Because no two residents'' needs are the same, no two plans are the same. We''ll help you customize your own care services plan from a full menu of personalized assisted living services.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Our Assisted Living in Elk Grove Care Options Include:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul class="two-column">\r\n    <li>Medication Supervision</li>\r\n    <li>Medical appointment Scheduling</li>\r\n    <li>Bathing Assistance</li>\r\n    <li>Dressing and Personal Grooming Assistance</li>\r\n    <li>Escort to Meals and Activities</li>\r\n    <li>Ambulation Assistance</li>\r\n    <li>Incontinence Management</li>\r\n    <li>Diabetic Management Assistance</li>\r\n    <li>Special Diets</li>\r\n    <li>Laundry Service</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Amenities Include:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul class="two-column">\r\n    <li>Three Chef-Prepared Meals Daily&nbsp;</li>\r\n    <li>Scheduled Transportation</li>\r\n    <li>Health Monitoring</li>\r\n    <li>Apartment Maintenance</li>\r\n    <li>Weekly Housekeeping Services</li>\r\n    <li>All Utilities - Except Telephone - Including Cable TV</li>\r\n    <li>24-Hour Emergency Response</li>\r\n    <li>Comprehensive Activity Program</li>\r\n    <li>Recreational and Social Events</li>\r\n    <li>Exercise and Wellness Programs</li>\r\n    <li>In-House Pharmacy</li>\r\n    <li>Beauty/Barber Shop</li>\r\n    <li>Private Dining Room</li>\r\n    <li>Guest Meals</li>\r\n    <li>Fitness Center</li>\r\n    <li>Landscaped Courtyard</li>\r\n    <li>Pet Friendly Community</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Assisted Living', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '260-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-09-10 19:26:18', '2014-09-10 19:26:18', '', 260, 'http://www.estanciads.com/redesign/260-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(207, 2, '2014-08-22 17:45:18', '2014-08-22 17:45:18', '<p class="intro-text">Senior living communities with a difference: a true sense of belonging.</p>\r\n<h3>ARIZONA</h3>\r\n<h4><a href="http://www.mcdowellvillage.com/" target="_blank">McDowell Village</a></h4>\r\n<p>McDowell Village is a 207 unit independent and assisted living community located in South Scottsdale - &frac14; mile west of highway 101 and 2 miles east of highway 202, which provides access to downtown Phoenix. The Community benefits from the City of Scottsdale sponsored 38,000 square foot Granite Reef Senior Center, which provides educational, recreational and social activities.&nbsp;<a href="http://www.mcdowellvillage.com/" target="_blank">MORE &#8594;</a></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3>CALIFORNIA</h3>\r\n<h4><a href="http://www.commonsatelkgrove.com/" target="_blank">The Commons at Elk Grove</a></h4>\r\n<p>The Commons at Elk Grove is a 95 unit independent, assisted living and memory care community conveniently located in the heart of Elk Grove. Residents enjoy private, spacious studios, one-and two-bedroom suites surrounded by their own furniture and personal treasures. Residents have a place to call their own. Cozy yet elegant surroundings, stimulating activities and excursions, exceptional amenities and extra help when needed-you''ll find all this and more at The Commons at Elk Grove Assisted Living Community. <a href="http://www.commonsatelkgrove.com/" target="_blank">MORE &#8594;</a></p>\r\n\r\n<h4><a href="http://www.commonsonthornton.com" target="_blank">The Commons on Thornton</a></h4>\r\n<p>The Commons on Thornton is a 100 unit independent, assisted living and memory care community conveniently located in the heart of the Central Valley. Residents enjoy private, spacious studios, one-and two-bedroom suites surrounded by their own furniture and personal treasures. Residents have a place to call their own. Cozy yet elegant surroundings, stimulating activities and excursions, exceptional amenities and extra help when needed-you''ll find all this and more at The Commons&nbsp;on Thornton&nbsp;Assisted Living Community. <a href="http://www.commonsonthornton.com" target="_blank">MORE &#8594;</a></p>\r\n\r\n<h4><a href="http://www.commonsatunionranch.com" target="_blank">The Commons at Union Ranch</a></h4>\r\n<p>The Commons at Union Ranch is a 98 unit independent, assisted living and memory care community conveniently located in the heart of the Central Valley. Residents enjoy private, spacious studios, one-and two-bedroom suites surrounded by their own furniture and personal treasures. Residents have a place to call their own. Cozy yet elegant surroundings, stimulating activities and excursions, exceptional amenities and extra help when needed-you''ll find all this and more at The Commons at Union Ranch Assisted Living Community. <a href="http://www.commonsatunionranch.com" target="_blank">MORE &#8594;</a></p>\r\n\r\n<h4><a href="http://www.dalecommons.com" target="_blank">Dale Commons</a></h4>\r\n<p>Dale Commons is a 98 unit independent and assisted living community located in the heart of Stanislaus County, Modesto. Residents enjoy private, spacious studios, one-and two-bedroom suites surrounded by their own furniture and personal treasures. Residents have a place to call their own. Cozy yet elegant surroundings, stimulating activities and excursions, exceptional amenities and extra help when needed-you''ll find all this and more at Dale Commons Assisted Living Community. <a href="http://www.dalecommons.com" target="_blank">MORE &#8594;</a></p>\r\n\r\n<h4><a href="http://www.estanciads.com" target="_blank">Estancia Del Sol</a></h4>\r\n<p>Estancia Del Sol is a 117 unit independent, assisted living and memory care community conveniently located in the heart of Corona, CA. Residents enjoy private, spacious studios, one-and two-bedroom suites surrounded by their own furniture and personal treasures. Residents have a place to call their own. Cozy yet elegant surroundings, stimulating activities and excursions, exceptional amenities and extra help when needed-you''ll find all this and more at Estancia Del Sol Assisted Living Community. <a href="http://www.estanciads.com" target="_blank">MORE &#8594;</a></p>\r\n\r\n<h4><a href="http://www.thereserveatthousandoaks.com" target="_blank">The Reserve at Thousand Oaks</a></h4>\r\n<p>The Reserve at Thousand Oaks is a 140 unit independent and assisted living community occupying a magnificent hilltop site in Thousand Oaks, affording breathtaking views of the entire Conejos Valley and the Santa Rosa foothills. The Ventura freeway is less than 10 minutes from your door and the Pacific Ocean is only 30 minutes to the south through the beautiful Santa Monica Mountains. <a href="http://www.thereserveatthousandoaks.com" target="_blank">MORE &#8594;</a></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3>WASHINGTON</h3>\r\n<h4><a href="http://www.thebellettini.com" target="_blank">The Bellettini</a></h4>\r\n<p>The Bellettini offers 145 senior apartment homes for those over the age of 62, featuring 25 different floor plans only steps away from the energy and buzz of downtown Bellevue, within the calm and comfort of residential living. One- and two-bedroom apartments range from 700 square feet to 2,400 square feet. Assisted living services can be added and customized at any time. <a href="http://www.thebellettini.com" target="_blank">MORE &#8594;</a></p>', 'Communities', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '10-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-08-22 17:45:18', '2014-08-22 17:45:18', '', 10, 'http://new.westliving.net/10-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(208, 3, '2014-08-25 16:00:44', '2014-08-25 16:00:44', '<strong>CORONA, CA (August 25, 2014)</strong> Estancia Del Sol, WESTliving’s newest senior living community is pleased to announce the opening of their Leasing Center.  The Leasing Center is open 7 days a week from 9:00 a.m. to 5:00 p.m. and welcomes prospective residents and families to drop by for a glimpse of the exceptional lifestyle, amenities and innovative programs Estancia Del Sol has to offer.  This new development broke ground in November 2013, and is slated to be complete in December 2014.\r\n\r\n“Interest level has exceeded expectations”, says Carrie Compton, sales director.  “The Marketing team is already taking reservations for preferred locations.  And a sneak preview “Dusty Shoe” event will be scheduled in September for the general public.”\r\n\r\nReminiscent of a fine Spanish estate, the new master planned community, Estancia Del Sol will consist of 91 assisted living and 26 memory care apartments.  The community is conveniently located with easy freeway access and is in close proximity to many shopping amenities.\r\n\r\n“While the opening of the building itself is scheduled for December of this year, one can already see the elegant design of the apartments and superior construction workmanship,” says General Manager Sam Faye. “We are very proud of our newly built “flagship” community.”\r\n\r\nEstancia Del Sol is a private-pay community with monthly fees starting at $2,650 per month. The monthly fee includes three daily chef-prepared meals, weekly housekeeping and linen service, transportation, and engaging activities including exercise classes in the fitness center, and 24 hour staffing.\r\n\r\n“Estancia Del Sol will bring a hospitality and boutique feel that will redefine senior living – a philosophy like this may not be what you’d expect from senior living, but we imagine seniors living in Corona will enjoy getting used to it.” says Patrick Collins, vice president of operations.\r\n\r\n<h3>About WESTliving</h3>\r\n\r\nWESTliving was formed in early 2009 to own and operate hospitality based senior living communities providing an exceptional variety of lifestyles, wellness, and care options. Located in Carlsbad, California, WESTliving owns and operates within the Pacific and Southwest regions of the United States. From independent living through assisted living, WESTliving combines comfortable elegance with attentive, world-class service, the result? A true sense of belonging for seniors and their families. Find out what senior living was meant to be. More information about WESTliving can be found at <a href="http://www.WESTliving.net">www.WESTliving.net</a>.\r\n\r\n<h4>Media Contact:</h4>\r\nContact: Sam Faye\r\nEmail:<a href="mailto:smfaye@estanciads.com">smfaye@estanciads.com</a>	\r\nT 951.340.3200\r\n\r\n<h4>Community Information:</h4>\r\nEstancia Del Sol\r\n2489 California Avenue\r\nCorona, CA  92881\r\nT 951.340.3200\r\n\r\n', 'Estancia Del Sol''s Leasing Center is Now Open', '', 'trash', 'open', 'closed', '', 'estancia-del-sols-leasing-center-now-open', '', '', '2014-11-18 21:24:35', '2014-11-18 21:24:35', '', 0, 'http://new.westliving.net/?p=208', 0, 'post', '', 0),
