(215, 1, '2014-05-02 22:51:58', '2014-05-02 22:51:58', '<h3>Location: Stockton, CA</h3>\r\n<h2>Position Summary:</h2>\r\n\r\nThe Commons on Thornton is seeking an experienced individual for the position of Bus Driver. This is a part time position and must be able to work weekends.\r\n\r\nReporting to the Activities Director, the Bus Driver will provide safe transportation for residents to and from medical appointments, shopping, banking and special functions planned by the Activities Director.\r\n\r\nWESTliving is looking to fill this position with a person who possesses the following talents:\r\n\r\n<strong>Achiever</strong> – self driven and motivated by achieving defined stated goals.\r\n<strong>Arranger</strong> – possesses an ability to direct and lead others to accomplish the company’s business objectives.\r\n<strong>Strategic Thinker</strong> – demonstrates an ability to think and play out alternative scenarios and determine a correct course of action and give others a picture of the future.\r\n<strong>Problem Solver</strong> – someone who can find solutions and keep things moving, even with incomplete information.\r\n<strong>Persuasiveness</strong> – an ability to work with others and take them in a direction that is complementary to the Company’s objectives.\r\n\r\nIn addition to the talents listed above WESTliving is looking to fill this position with a person who possesses the following:\r\n<h3>Skills</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Inspect bus each morning and fill out “Vehicle Inspection good running condition Form” approved by the California Highway Patrol. This includes checking the essential fluids (power steering, transmission, coolant). Checking the tires for wear and tear and proper inflation. Checking the condition of the body for scratches and dents and keeping the exterior clean. Making sure the interior is clean and free of obstruction that may be a hazard to passengers.</li>\r\n	<li>Washing windshield and other windows that may need cleaning so the driver has an unobstructed view.</li>\r\n	<li>Checking the seatbelt latches and webbing for wear that may weaken the integrity of the belt.</li>\r\n	<li>Checking the wheelchair restraints for wear and malfunctions.</li>\r\n	<li>Checking the wheelchair lift for proper fluid level and proper operation so as to provide a safe and secure feeling for use by residents. Know how to operate the lift in a safe and confident manner. Know how to operate the lift in case of power failure on the bus. This includes the correct use of the manual handle to lower and raise the lift.</li>\r\n	<li>Keep Maintenance Records on approved forms as required by the California Highway Patrol. This includes the daily inspection record and routine maintenance performed at appropriate time and mileage intervals as required by the California Highway Patrol.</li>\r\n	<li>Be informed about any changes in the Motor Vehicle Code as they apply to the operation of the bus.</li>\r\n	<li>Know how to fill out various forms as they apply to operation of the bus such as Accident Report.</li>\r\n	<li>Coordinate trips with the Activity Director and other departments as needed.</li>\r\n	<li>Assist is activities as assigned.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Knowledge</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Possess at least one year to two years of experience</li>\r\n	<li>Must have a valid California Class "B" operator''s license with "Passenger Endorsement" and a current Medical Examiner''s certificate.</li>\r\n	<li>Must be able to read written direction, comprehend verbal instructions, and write at a level necessary to accomplish the job.</li>\r\n	<li>Must be capable of maintaining regular attendance.</li>\r\n	<li>Must have an acceptable driving record substantiated by a California DMV print out for the previous ten years.</li>\r\n	<li>CPR and First Aid trained required.</li>\r\n	<li>Will have a criminal record clearance prior to presence in the facility.</li>\r\n	<li>Must meet all health requirements, including TB, and pass background checks.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Driver', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'driver-commons-thornton', '', '', '2014-08-29 16:05:14', '2014-08-29 16:05:14', '', 0, 'http://www.westliving.net/test/?post_type=careers&#038;p=215', 0, 'careers', '', 0),
