(223, 2, '2014-08-27 23:17:37', '2014-08-27 23:17:37', '<p class="intro-text">Senior living retirement communities with a difference: a true sense of belonging.</p>\r\n<h3>ARIZONA</h3>\r\n<h4><a href="http://www.mcdowellvillage.com/" target="_blank">McDowell Village</a></h4>\r\n<p>McDowell Village is a 207 unit independent and assisted living community located in South Scottsdale - &frac14; mile west of highway 101 and 2 miles east of highway 202, which provides access to downtown Phoenix. The Community benefits from the City of Scottsdale sponsored 38,000 square foot Granite Reef Senior Center, which provides educational, recreational and social activities.&nbsp;<a href="http://www.mcdowellvillage.com/" target="_blank">MORE &#8594;</a></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3>CALIFORNIA</h3>\r\n<h4><a href="http://www.commonsatelkgrove.com/" target="_blank">The Commons at Elk Grove</a></h4>\r\n<p>The Commons at Elk Grove is a 95 unit independent, assisted living and memory care community conveniently located in the heart of Elk Grove. Residents enjoy private, spacious studios, one-and two-bedroom suites surrounded by their own furniture and personal treasures. Residents have a place to call their own. Cozy yet elegant surroundings, stimulating activities and excursions, exceptional amenities and extra help when needed-you''ll find all this and more at The Commons at Elk Grove Assisted Living Community. <a href="http://www.commonsatelkgrove.com/" target="_blank">MORE &#8594;</a></p>\r\n\r\n<h4><a href="http://www.commonsonthornton.com" target="_blank">The Commons on Thornton</a></h4>\r\n<p>The Commons on Thornton is a 100 unit independent, assisted living and memory care community conveniently located in the heart of the Central Valley. Residents enjoy private, spacious studios, one-and two-bedroom suites surrounded by their own furniture and personal treasures. Residents have a place to call their own. Cozy yet elegant surroundings, stimulating activities and excursions, exceptional amenities and extra help when needed-you''ll find all this and more at The Commons&nbsp;on Thornton&nbsp;Assisted Living Community. <a href="http://www.commonsonthornton.com" target="_blank">MORE &#8594;</a></p>\r\n\r\n<h4><a href="http://www.commonsatunionranch.com" target="_blank">The Commons at Union Ranch</a></h4>\r\n<p>The Commons at Union Ranch is a 98 unit independent, assisted living and memory care community conveniently located in the heart of the Central Valley. Residents enjoy private, spacious studios, one-and two-bedroom suites surrounded by their own furniture and personal treasures. Residents have a place to call their own. Cozy yet elegant surroundings, stimulating activities and excursions, exceptional amenities and extra help when needed-you''ll find all this and more at The Commons at Union Ranch Assisted Living Community. <a href="http://www.commonsatunionranch.com" target="_blank">MORE &#8594;</a></p>\r\n\r\n<h4><a href="http://www.dalecommons.com" target="_blank">Dale Commons</a></h4>\r\n<p>Dale Commons is a 98 unit independent and assisted living community located in the heart of Stanislaus County, Modesto. Residents enjoy private, spacious studios, one-and two-bedroom suites surrounded by their own furniture and personal treasures. Residents have a place to call their own. Cozy yet elegant surroundings, stimulating activities and excursions, exceptional amenities and extra help when needed-you''ll find all this and more at Dale Commons Assisted Living Community. <a href="http://www.dalecommons.com" target="_blank">MORE &#8594;</a></p>\r\n\r\n<h4><a href="http://www.estanciads.com" target="_blank">Estancia Del Sol</a></h4>\r\n<p>Estancia Del Sol is a 117 unit independent, assisted living and memory care community conveniently located in the heart of Corona, CA. Residents enjoy private, spacious studios, one-and two-bedroom suites surrounded by their own furniture and personal treasures. Residents have a place to call their own. Cozy yet elegant surroundings, stimulating activities and excursions, exceptional amenities and extra help when needed-you''ll find all this and more at Estancia Del Sol Assisted Living Community. <a href="http://www.estanciads.com" target="_blank">MORE &#8594;</a></p>\r\n\r\n<h4><a href="http://www.thereserveatthousandoaks.com" target="_blank">The Reserve at Thousand Oaks</a></h4>\r\n<p>The Reserve at Thousand Oaks is a 140 unit independent and assisted living community occupying a magnificent hilltop site in Thousand Oaks, affording breathtaking views of the entire Conejos Valley and the Santa Rosa foothills. The Ventura freeway is less than 10 minutes from your door and the Pacific Ocean is only 30 minutes to the south through the beautiful Santa Monica Mountains. <a href="http://www.thereserveatthousandoaks.com" target="_blank">MORE &#8594;</a></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3>WASHINGTON</h3>\r\n<h4><a href="http://www.thebellettini.com" target="_blank">The Bellettini</a></h4>\r\n<p>The Bellettini offers 145 senior apartment homes for those over the age of 62, featuring 25 different floor plans only steps away from the energy and buzz of downtown Bellevue, within the calm and comfort of residential living. One- and two-bedroom apartments range from 700 square feet to 2,400 square feet. Assisted living services can be added and customized at any time. <a href="http://www.thebellettini.com" target="_blank">MORE &#8594;</a></p>', 'Communities', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '10-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-08-27 23:17:37', '2014-08-27 23:17:37', '', 10, 'http://www.westliving.net/10-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(625, 2, '2014-11-05 22:42:22', '2014-11-05 22:42:22', '<div class="row">\r\n    <div class="col-sm-3"><img class="margin-top-10" src="/wp-content/uploads/sam-faye.jpg" alt="Sam Faye" /></div>\r\n    <div class="col-sm-9">\r\n        <h2>Sam Faye</h2>\r\n        <h4>General Manager</h4>\r\n        As our General Manager, Sam Faye brings senior housing hospitality leadership to a new level at Estancia Del Sol.  With over 20 years of diverse experience from both the senior housing and hospitality industries, Sam leads our team of service professionals.  Sam’s award-winning background includes pioneer work in establishing market awareness with successful openings of new senior housing communities in California.  His customer engagement, organizational skills, and attention to detail sets the bar high through a team approach to service delivery.  Sam developed his hospitality roots in many well-known lodging organizations, acting as the catalyst to apply his hospitality expertise to an older adult customer in early 2000.  He is a hands-on leader in supporting his team, while fostering operational plans for success.  Sam prides himself on building exceptional teams and delivering legendary service.  Couple this with his genuine sense of humor and quick wit to put anyone at ease, and we are confident you’ll experience memorable moments at Estancia Del Sol.\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row">\r\n    <div class="col-sm-3"><img class="margin-top-10" src="/wp-content/uploads/carrie-compton.jpg" alt="Carrie Compton" /></div>\r\n    <div class="col-sm-9">\r\n        <h2>Carrie Compton</h2>\r\n        <h4>Sales Director</h4>\r\n        When you meet Carrie Compton, our Sales Director, you’ll quickly realize that she demonstrates genuine interest and compassion for serving older adults.  She not only is a wonderful listener, she is attentive in understanding unique desires and interests of others.  Her many years in senior housing sales draw upon the exploratory, the unique, the passions of others – creating solutions and options the customer can experience as a customized housing and amenities match distinct to them.  Carrie provides the right level of service to ultimately find that special place older adults can call home.  You can personally experience this for yourself – so come on in so she can show you around!  She welcomes the chance to spend some time with you and see how Estancia Del Sol can fulfill your desires and create the unexpected.\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row">\r\n    <div class="col-sm-3"><img class="margin-top-10" src="/wp-content/uploads/stephen-pratt.jpg" alt="Stephen Pratt" /></div>\r\n    <div class="col-sm-9">\r\n        <h2>Stephen Pratt</h2>\r\n        <h4>Marketing Liaison</h4>\r\n        Stephen’s goal as Marketing Liaison is bringing our amenities and services to light in the greater market of Corona and the surrounding area.  Stephen works closely with Carrie in sales through education about our community, relationship building with referral sources, and educating all who are willing to hear about what Estancia Del Sol is all about.  Stephen draws upon two areas to get the word out about Estancia Del Sol: Through his many roles in growing up in the business in other senior housing communities, as well as his sincere interest to educate older adults and professionals working with seniors in truly understanding how Estancia Del Sol offers opportunities to enjoy a better quality of life.  You may have encountered Stephen through a presentation to a group or through an introduction by your health care professional.  Either way, he sees the best part of his role was accomplished with a better understanding of how we can help!\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>', 'Meet Our Team', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '22-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-11-05 22:42:22', '2014-11-05 22:42:22', '', 22, 'http://www.estanciads.com/22-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(626, 2, '2014-11-05 23:20:15', '2014-11-05 23:20:15', '', 'allen-johnson', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', 'allen-johnson', '', '', '2014-11-05 23:20:15', '2014-11-05 23:20:15', '', 0, 'http://www.estanciads.com/wp-content/uploads/allen-johnson.jpg', 0, 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', 0),
(628, 7, '2014-11-05 23:33:34', '2014-11-05 23:33:34', '<div class="row">\r\n<div class="col-sm-3"><img class="margin-top-10" src="/wp-content/uploads/sam-faye.jpg" alt="Sam Faye" /></div>\r\n<div class="col-sm-9">\r\n<h2>Sam Faye</h2>\r\n<h4>General Manager</h4>\r\nAs our General Manager, Sam Faye brings senior housing hospitality leadership to a new level at Estancia Del Sol. With over 20 years of diverse experience from both the senior housing and hospitality industries, Sam leads our team of service professionals. Sam’s award-winning background includes pioneer work in establishing market awareness with successful openings of new senior housing communities in California. His customer engagement, organizational skills, and attention to detail sets the bar high through a team approach to service delivery. Sam developed his hospitality roots in many well-known lodging organizations, acting as the catalyst to apply his hospitality expertise to an older adult customer in early 2000. He is a hands-on leader in supporting his team, while fostering operational plans for success. Sam prides himself on building exceptional teams and delivering legendary service. Couple this with his genuine sense of humor and quick wit to put anyone at ease, and we are confident you’ll experience memorable moments at Estancia Del Sol.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="col-sm-3"><img class="margin-top-10" src="/wp-content/uploads/carrie-compton.jpg" alt="Carrie Compton" /></div>\r\n<div class="col-sm-9">\r\n<h2>Carrie Compton</h2>\r\n<h4>Sales Director</h4>\r\nWhen you meet Carrie Compton, our Sales Director, you’ll quickly realize that she demonstrates genuine interest and compassion for serving older adults. She''s not only a wonderful listener, she is attentive in understanding unique desires and interests of others. Her many years in senior housing sales draw upon the exploratory, the unique, the passions of others – creating solutions and options the customer can experience as a customized housing and amenities match distinct to them. Carrie provides the right level of service to ultimately find that special place older adults can call home. You can personally experience this for yourself – so come on in so she can show you around! She welcomes the chance to spend some time with you and see how Estancia Del Sol can fulfill your desires and create the unexpected.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="col-sm-3"><img class="margin-top-10" src="/wp-content/uploads/stephen-pratt.jpg" alt="Stephen Pratt" /></div>\r\n<div class="col-sm-9">\r\n<h2>Stephen Pratt</h2>\r\n<h4>Marketing Liaison</h4>\r\nStephen’s goal as Marketing Liaison is bringing our amenities and services to light in the greater market of Corona and the surrounding area. Stephen works closely with Carrie in sales through education about our community, relationship building with referral sources, and educating all who are willing to hear about what Estancia Del Sol is all about. Stephen draws upon two areas to get the word out about Estancia Del Sol: Through his many roles in growing up in the business in other senior housing communities, as well as his sincere interest to educate older adults and professionals working with seniors in truly understanding how Estancia Del Sol offers opportunities to enjoy a better quality of life. You may have encountered Stephen through a presentation to a group or through an introduction by your health care professional. Either way, he sees the best part of his role was accomplished with a better understanding of how we can help!\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="col-sm-3"><img class="margin-top-10" src="/wp-content/uploads/allen-johnson.jpg" alt="Allen Johnson" /></div>\r\n<div class="col-sm-9">\r\n<h2>Allen Johnson</h2>\r\n<h4>Food &amp; Beverage Director</h4>\r\nAllen would describe his role in humble terms, but that would not do justice to his culinary direction and expertise 