(615, 2, '2014-10-27 23:37:00', '2014-10-27 23:37:00', 'Less than a year ago construction of Estancia Del Sol broke ground. Now instead of wooden frames and dirt, the community and landscape are taking shape. Interior walls are in place, windows have been installed and the stone finishes are close to completion throughout the property.\r\n\r\nThe Marketing team and General Manager are thrilled with the tremendous interest in their community. Future residents are already beginning to pick out their preferred units. Carrie Compton, Sales Director, stated, “This property is state of the art, and will give a true sense of belonging – making you feel right at home. We will have phenomenal programing to keep our residents engaged and healthy!”\r\n\r\nStarting at just $2,650 a month, residents enjoy three restaurant style meals, high-end amenities and WESTclass hospitality every day. Come visit the leasing center and find out more of what Estancia Del Sol will have to offer!\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<div class="col-md-3">\r\n<a href="http://www.estanciads.com/wp-content/uploads/construction-update-91014-1.jpg" rel="lightbox" alt="" title=""><img src="http://www.estanciads.com/wp-content/uploads/construction-update-thumb-1.jpg" alt="construction-update-thumb-1" width="176" height="176" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-557" alt="" title="" /></a>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-3">\r\n<a href="http://www.estanciads.com/wp-content/uploads/construction-update-91014-2.jpg" rel="lightbox" alt="" title=""><img src="http://www.estanciads.com/wp-content/uploads/construction-update-thumb-2.jpg" alt="construction-update-thumb-2" width="176" height="176" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-558" alt="" title="" /></a>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-3">\r\n<a href="http://www.estanciads.com/wp-content/uploads/construction-update-91014-3.jpg" rel="lightbox" alt="" title=""><img src="http://www.estanciads.com/wp-content/uploads/construction-update-thumb-3.jpg" alt="construction-update-thumb-3" width="176" height="176" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-559" alt="" title="" /></a>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-3">\r\n<a href="http://www.estanciads.com/wp-content/uploads/construction-update-91014-4.jpg" rel="lightbox" alt="" title=""><img src="http://www.estanciads.com/wp-content/uploads/construction-update-thumb-4.jpg" alt="construction-update-thumb-4" width="176" height="176" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-560" alt="" title="" /></a>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'Estancia Del Sol transforming before your eyes!', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '550-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-10-27 23:37:00', '2014-10-27 23:37:00', '', 550, 'http://www.estanciads.com/550-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(327, 2, '2014-09-10 17:08:49', '2014-09-10 17:08:49', '<p class="intro-text">Isn''t it time you spent time with people as interesting as you?</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Be yourself. You''re right where you belong.</h3>\r\n\r\nHe says tomato. She says tomahto. And that''s exactly what makes things interesting around here. By embracing everyone''s uniqueness, we''ve created a community where everyone feels like they belong. That''s why here at The Commons at Elk Grove, you can choose the lifestyle option that fits you. Choose from Elk Grove senior care options including independent living, living that offers assistance with your everyday routine, Alzheimer''s and dementia care or respite care. Plus our wide range of amenities and activities means there''s always something to inspire, excite, relax or intrigue. Why let another day go by without learning tai chi? Without taking up watercolors? Without strolling the garden? Don''t worry, we have the details covered. All you have to do is enjoy. ', 'Senior Care Living Options', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '10-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-09-10 17:08:49', '2014-09-10 17:08:49', '', 10, 'http://www.estanciads.com/redesign/10-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(240, 2, '2014-08-29 23:43:09', '2014-08-29 23:43:09', '<p class="intro-text">Senior living retirement communities with a difference: a true sense of belonging.</p>\r\n<h3>ARIZONA</h3>\r\n<h4><a href="http://www.mcdowellvillage.com/" target="_blank">McDowell Village</a></h4>\r\n<p>McDowell Village is a 207 unit independent and assisted living community located in South Scottsdale - &frac14; mile west of highway 101 and 2 miles east of highway 202, which provides access to downtown Phoenix. The Community benefits from the City of Scottsdale sponsored 38,000 square foot Granite Reef Senior Center, which provides educational, recreational and social activities.&nbsp;<a href="http://www.mcdowellvillage.com/" target="_blank">MORE &#8594;</a></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3>CALIFORNIA</h3>\r\n<h4><a href="http://www.commonsatelkgrove.com/" target="_blank">The Commons at Elk Grove</a></h4>\r\n<p>The Commons at Elk Grove is a 95 unit independent, assisted living and memory care community conveniently located in the heart of Elk Grove. Residents enjoy private, spacious studios, one-and two-bedroom suites surrounded by their own furniture and personal treasures. Residents have a place to call their own. Cozy yet elegant surroundings, stimulating activities and excursions, exceptional amenities and extra help when needed-you''ll find all this and more at The Commons at Elk Grove Assisted Living Community. <a href="http://www.commonsatelkgrove.com/" target="_blank">MORE &#8594;</a></p>\r\n\r\n<h4><a href="http://www.commonsonthornton.com" target="_blank">The Commons on Thornton</a></h4>\r\n<p>The Commons on Thornton is a 100 unit independent, assisted living and memory care community conveniently located in the heart of the Central Valley. Residents enjoy private, spacious studios, one-and two-bedroom suites surrounded by their own furniture and personal treasures. Residents have a place to call their own. Cozy yet elegant surroundings, stimulating activities and excursions, exceptional amenities and extra help when needed-you''ll find all this and more at The Commons&nbsp;on Thornton&nbsp;Assisted Living Community. <a href="http://www.commonsonthornton.com" target="_blank">MORE &#8594;</a></p>\r\n\r\n<h4><a href="http://www.commonsatunionranch.com" target="_blank">The Commons at Union Ranch</a></h4>\r\n<p>The Commons at Union Ranch is a 98 unit independent, assisted living and memory care community conveniently located in the heart of the Central Valley. Residents enjoy private, spacious studios, one-and two-bedroom suites surrounded by their own furniture and personal treasures. Residents have a place to call their own. Cozy yet elegant surroundings, stimulating activities and excursions, exceptional amenities and extra help when needed-you''ll find all this and more at The Commons at Union Ranch Assisted Living Community. <a href="http://www.commonsatunionranch.com" target="_blank">MORE &#8594;</a></p>\r\n\r\n<h4><a href="http://www.dalecommons.com" target="_blank">Dale Commons</a></h4>\r\n<p>Dale Commons is a 98 unit independent and assisted living community located in the heart of Stanislaus County, Modesto. Residents enjoy private, spacious studios, one-and two-bedroom suites surrounded by their own furniture and personal treasures. Residents have a place to call their own. Cozy yet elegant surroundings, stimulating activities and excursions, exceptional amenities and extra help when needed-you''ll find all this and more at Dale Commons Assisted Living Community. <a href="http://www.dalecommons.com" target="_blank">MORE &#8594;</a></p>\r\n\r\n<h4><a href="http://www.estanciads.com" target="_blank">Estancia Del Sol</a></h4>\r\n<p>Estancia Del Sol is a 117 unit independent, assisted living and memory care community conveniently located in the heart of Corona, CA. Residents enjoy private, spacious studios, one-and two-bedroom suites surrounded by their own furniture and personal treasures. Residents have a place to call their own. Cozy yet elegant surroundings, stimulating activities and excursions, exceptional amenities and extra help when needed-you''ll find all this and more at Estancia Del Sol Assisted Living Community. <a href="http://www.estanciads.com" target="_blank">MORE &#8594;</a></p>\r\n\r\n<h4><a href="http://www.thereserveatthousandoaks.com" target="_blank">The Reserve at Thousand Oaks</a></h4>\r\n<p>The Reserve at Thousand Oaks is a 140 unit independent and assisted living community occupying a magnificent hilltop site in Thousand Oaks, affording breathtaking views of the entire Conejos Valley and the Santa Rosa foothills. The Ventura freeway is less than 10 minutes from your door and the Pacific Ocean is only 30 minutes to the south through the beautiful Santa Monica Mountains. <a href="http://www.thereserveatthousandoaks.com" target="_blank">MORE &#8594;</a></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3>WASHINGTON</h3>\r\n<h4><a href="http://www.thebellettini.com" target="_blank">The Bellettini</a></h4>\r\n<p>The Bellettini offers 145 senior apartment homes for those over the age of 62, featuring 25 different floor plans only steps away from the energy and buzz of downtown Bellevue, within the calm and comfort of residential living. One- and two-bedroom apartments range from 700 square feet to 2,400 square feet. Assisted living services can be added and customized at any time. <a href="http://www.thebellettini.com" target="_blank">MORE &#8594;</a></p>', 'Living Options', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '10-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-08-29 23:43:09', '2014-08-29 23:43:09', '', 10, 'http://www.estanciads.com/redesign/10-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(246, 2, '2014-09-04 17:01:25', '2014-09-04 17:01:25', '<p class="intro-text">At WESTliving our mission centers on delivering exceptional services and experiences by inspiring and empowering our Team Members to make a meaningful difference in the lives of those we serve.  WESTliving’s culture is grounded in the fact that these daily actions and behaviors support our shared vision to be the most respected and recognized service company in the world.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>WESTliving was formed in early 2009 to own and operate hospitality based senior living communities providing exceptional variety of lifestyles, wellness, and care options. WESTclass uncompromising quality is apparent with respect to building standards, amenities, Team Member’s commitment, as well as the integration of innovative programs and wellness options designed to accommodate and support an array of lifestyles and needs.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The WESTclass Team of talented and experienced leaders in the industry bring a customer centered approach to senior living. Team members are driven by WESTliving Core Values, Mission, and Service Standards as guiding principles to be engaged, responsible and attentive to all we serve in achieving our Vision.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>WESTliving is located in Carlsbad, California and operates within the Pacific and Southwest regions of the United States. Maintaining a boutique and uniquely focused approached as a regional operator enables WESTliving to stay true to its vision of service excellence.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>At WESTliving, we make it easy for residents to remain a part of the larger community just outside their door. This is why we reach out into the neighborhood to support and partner with cultural centers, schools and senior advocacy groups, to name a few. You will find intergenerational experiences, philanthropy and good ol’ neighborliness alive and well. This is what we call a true sense of belonging.</p>', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '12-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-09-04 17:01:25', '2014-09-04 17:01:25', '', 12, 'http://www.estanciads.com/redesign/12-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
