(258, 2, '2014-09-04 17:40:48', '2014-09-04 17:40:48', 'INDEPENDENT LIVING, SCOTTSDALE STYLE.\r\n\r\n<h3>This is what independent living was meant to be.</h3>\r\nYou''ve worked hard. Now it''s time to reap the rewards. And what better place than in a beautiful Scottsdale community filled with interesting neighbors, new friends and ever-attentive service? \r\n\r\nAt McDowell Village, community spaces are more than extensions of your home, they''re extensions of your life. Here, you''ll find the inviting, the comfortable, even the extraordinary. Our state-of-the art gym will build your body and spirit with cardio and strength training, yoga, tai chi and other alternative programs. After your workout, step outside for a relaxing soak in the jacuzzi or lounge by the pool with friends. Still full of energy? Feel free to join an instructor-led aquatics class.\r\n\r\nOur computer lounge makes it easy to download photos, email, catch up on Facebook, research your next exciting travel adventure or try out our brain fitness program. After a full day like this, be sure to pamper yourself with a manicure or pedicure in the salon.\r\n\r\nNext, imagine walking into the dining room and seeing your famous homemade spaghetti on the dinner menu. Or sitting down in the in-house movie theater as your very favorite movie begins to play. We didn''t read your mind, but you''ll feel like we did. Because we take the time to get to know you as a person. Small, meaningful touches are a way of life around here.\r\n\r\n*Independent Living at <strong>McDowell Village</strong> in Scottsdale. You could get used to this.*\r\n', 'Independent Living', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'independent-living', '', '', '2014-11-19 21:20:52', '2014-11-19 21:20:52', '', 10, 'http://www.estanciads.com/redesign/?page_id=258', 0, 'page', '', 0),
