(260, 2, '2014-09-04 17:41:04', '2014-09-04 17:41:04', '<strong>RESPECTFUL ASSISTED LIVING </strong>\r\n<h3>Just because you want a little hand now and then doesn''t mean you can''t still lead.</h3>\r\nAt McDowell Village, assisted living means person-centered care. Because no two residents'' needs are the same, no two plans are the same. We''ll help you customize your own care services plan from a full menu of personalized assisted living services.\r\n\r\n<strong>McDowell Village Assisted Living in Scottsdale, Care Options Include:</strong>\r\n<ul class="two-column">\r\n	<li>Medication Supervision</li>\r\n	<li>Medical appointment Scheduling</li>\r\n	<li>Bathing Assistance</li>\r\n	<li>Dressing and Personal Grooming Assistance</li>\r\n	<li>Escort to Meals and Activities</li>\r\n	<li>Ambulation Assistance</li>\r\n	<li>Incontinence Management</li>\r\n	<li>Diabetic Management Assistance</li>\r\n	<li>Special Diets</li>\r\n	<li>Laundry Service</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Amenities Include:</strong>\r\n<ul class="two-column">\r\n	<li>Three Chef-Prepared Meals Daily</li>\r\n	<li>Scheduled Transportation</li>\r\n	<li>Health Monitoring</li>\r\n	<li>Apartment Maintenance</li>\r\n	<li>Weekly Housekeeping Services</li>\r\n	<li>All Utilities - Except Telephone - Including Cable TV</li>\r\n	<li>24-Hour Caregiving Staff Access/Emergency Response</li>\r\n	<li>Comprehensive Activity Program</li>\r\n	<li>Recreational and Social Events</li>\r\n	<li>Exercise and Wellness Programs</li>\r\n	<li>In-House Pharmacy</li>\r\n	<li>Beauty/Barber Shop</li>\r\n	<li>Private Dining Room</li>\r\n	<li>Guest Meals</li>\r\n	<li>Fitness Center</li>\r\n	<li>Landscaped Courtyard</li>\r\n	<li>Pet Friendly Community</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Assisted Living', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'assisted-living', '', '', '2014-11-19 21:50:51', '2014-11-19 21:50:51', '', 10, 'http://www.estanciads.com/redesign/?page_id=260', 0, 'page', '', 0),
