(262, 2, '2014-09-04 17:41:25', '2014-09-04 17:41:25', '<h3>Corona Alzheimer''s or Dementia Care - A respectful, safe place to call home.</h3>\r\nAs part of the WESTliving family, Estancia Del Sol offers the Renaissance Memory Care program: a unique approach that blends years of Alzheimer''s and other related dementia care experience with contemporary research developed by leaders in the field.\r\n\r\nEvery Team Member throughout the community completes extensive training in the Renaissance Memory Care program. This creates a team approach to services in a consistently safe, respectful, compassionate, and supportive environment.\r\n\r\nOur primary focus is to create a home-like environment that encourages resident engagement in activities that draw on individual interests.  We collaborate with family members in customizing a plan that meets individual needs and desires, to enrich the daily life of Alzheimer''s or dementia residents. This close partnership with family, friends, volunteers and community groups is integral to the well-being of each resident.\r\n\r\n<strong>Memory, Alzheimer''s &amp; Dementia Care Services Include:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>High Team Member to Resident Ratios</li>\r\n	<li>24 Hour Specially Trained Team Members on Duty</li>\r\n	<li>Medication Management</li>\r\n	<li>Assistance with Activities of Daily Living</li>\r\n	<li>Individualized Care Management Programs</li>\r\n	<li>Balanced, Nutritious Meals Approved by a Nutritionist</li>\r\n	<li>Alzheimer''s and Dementia Family Support and Involvement</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Memory Care', '', 'trash', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'memory-care', '', '', '2014-11-14 22:16:19', '2014-11-14 22:16:19', '', 10, 'http://www.estanciads.com/redesign/?page_id=262', 0, 'page', '', 0),
