(278, 2, '2014-09-04 17:49:28', '2014-09-04 17:49:28', '<h3>At McDowell Village, body and mind are top of mind.</h3>\r\nEveryone knows that fitness is about improving muscle tone and other aspects of your physical appearance. But it also involves keeping your heart healthy with proper nutrition, and enhancing your mental and spiritual well-being through inner work. When you engage in physical activity, your brain releases hormones that result in increased energy and happiness.\r\n\r\nIn addition to weights and cardio, we offer programs to improve balance, agility and focus, like yoga and tai chi. If you love spending time in the pool, join us for an instructor-led aquatics class. Relax in the jacuzzi, then enjoy a muscle-soothing massage. You''ve earned it.', 'WESTfitness', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'westfitness-senior-fitness', '', '', '2014-11-25 23:23:20', '2014-11-25 23:23:20', '', 256, 'http://www.estanciads.com/redesign/?page_id=278', 0, 'page', '', 0),
