(345, 2, '2014-10-16 21:01:43', '2014-10-16 21:01:43', '<h3>Variety is the spice of breakfast, lunch and dinner - Estancia Del Sol Style</h3>\nWhat could be better than sitting down to a delicious meal made with fresh wholesome ingredients and farm-to-table produce? A menu full of tasty choices and flavors that excite the palate.  You''ll taste many flavorful options at our Estancia Restaurant, as our chefs prepare a variety of entrees at every meal.  So you can get what you''re craving every time.  Have a favorite personal recipe?  Share it with our Food &amp; Beverage Director and we''ll do our best to ensure that it''s offered on the menu.\n\nOf course, dining options aren''t confined to the menu or location.  Feel free to meet friends in our Estancia Restaurant or choose a continental option at The Bistro.  Just like our service offerings, you pick and we''ll create to provide the relaxing meal with you and your family. Retirement community dining at its best.', 'Restaurant Dining or Casual Bistro', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '274-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-10-16 21:01:43', '2014-10-16 21:01:43', '', 274, 'http://www.estanciads.com/redesign/274-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
