(323, 2, '2014-09-04 23:28:06', '2014-09-04 23:28:06', '<h3>Welcome to world-class service. Welcome to comfortable, elegant surroundings. Welcome to senior living, WESTliving style.</h3>\r\nLooking for a welcoming community with exceptional service in sunny, southern California? You''re right where you belong: Estancia Del Sol in Corona, California.\r\n\r\nHere at Estancia Del Sol, we''re dedicated to offering a true sense of belonging to seniors and their families. It''s a feeling you''ll notice the moment you''re invited to "make yourself at home" and continues through every thoughtful, personal detail.\r\n\r\nAs part of the WESTliving family, we understand the importance of world-class service. In fact, we even have a name for it: WESTclass service. We hire carefully and train extensively. The result? Team Members who are empowered to make a meaningful difference in the lives of those we serve. And inspired to anticipate your next need - before you even know you have a next need.\r\n\r\nFrom independent, assisted, memory, Alzheimer''s or respite care, our approach reinforces a sense of belonging by promoting privacy, dignity and a sense of empowerment. A variety of activities including gardening, art classes, local tours and tai chi await here at Estancia Del Sol, just a short drive from Los Angeles and the Cleveland National Forest.\r\n\r\nYour warm, welcoming place to call home awaits at our Corona senior living community. Call the number above or email us to set up a tour and experience our difference in person.\r\n\r\n[ssba_hide]', 'Estancia Del Sol', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-09-04 23:28:06', '2014-09-04 23:28:06', '', 2, 'http://www.estanciads.com/redesign/2-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(542, 2, '2014-10-10 20:26:26', '2014-10-10 20:26:26', '<h3>Make yourself at home.  After all, you are.</h3>\r\nEstancia Del Sol offers a wide variety of apartment layouts and styles.  Each spacious apartment is uniquely designed featuring quality craftsmanship, elegant finishes, state of the art modern amenities, and wonderful vistas of surrounding beautifully landscaped areas or majestic mountain views.  Choose from a charming studio, a comfortable one-bedroom apartment, larger one-bedroom apartment, or a spacious two-bedroom apartment (up to 1,000 s.f.).\r\n\r\nSee for yourself, using our interactive floor plan below.  You can easily view each apartment style and location with either a simple floor plan layout or a suggested furniture configuration you may consider.  Either way, you''ll find an apartment style you can call your own - or soon to be new home!\r\n<!--<div class="row">\r\n<div class="col-md-6 center-content">\r\n<h2>First Floor</h2>\r\n<a class="img-link" title="First Floor" href="/map/images/first-floor.png" rel="lightbox"><img class="image-border" src="/map/images/map-floor1-thumb.jpg" alt="First Floor Map" /></a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-6 center-content">\r\n<h2>Second Floor</h2>\r\n<a class="img-link" title="Second Floor" href="/map/images/second-floor.png" rel="lightbox"><img class="image-border" src="/map/images/map-floor2-thumb.jpg" alt="Second Floor Map" /></a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n-->\r\n[widget id="text-18"]', 'Floor Plans', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '266-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-10-10 20:26:26', '2014-10-10 20:26:26', '', 266, 'http://www.estanciads.com/redesign/266-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(334, 2, '2014-09-10 19:30:21', '2014-09-10 19:30:21', '<h3>A respectful, safe place to call home.</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>As part of the WESTliving family, The Commons at Elk Grove offers the Renaissance Memory Care program: a unique approach that blends years of Alzheimer''s and other related&nbsp;dementia care experience with contemporary research developed by leaders in the field.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Every Team Member from housekeeping to administrative services to kitchen staff completes extensive training in the Renaissance Memory Care program to create a consistently safe, respectful, compassionate, and supportive environment.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our primary focus is to create a home-like environment that promotes the resident’s remaining abilities. We collaborate with the resident’s family members to enrich the daily life of&nbsp;Alzheimer''s or dementia residents. This close partnership with family, friends, volunteers and community groups is integral to the well-being of each resident. &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong></strong><strong>Memory, Alzheimer''s &amp; Dementia Care Services Include:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>High Team Member to Resident Ratios</li>\r\n    <li>24 Hour Specially Trained&nbsp;Team Members&nbsp;on Duty</li>\r\n    <li>Medication Management</li>\r\n    <li>Assistance with Activities of Daily Living</li>\r\n    <li>Individualized Care Management Programs</li>\r\n    <li>Balanced, Nutritious Meals Approved by a Nutritionist</li>\r\n    <li>Alzheimer''s and Dementia Family Support and Involvement</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Memory Care', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '262-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-09-10 19:30:21', '2014-09-10 19:30:21', '', 262, 'http://www.estanciads.com/redesign/262-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(333, 2, '2014-09-10 19:28:24', '2014-09-10 19:28:24', '<h3>A respectful, safe place to call home.</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>As part of the WESTliving family, The Commons at Elk Grove offers the Renaissance Memory Care program: a unique approach that blends years of Alzheimer''s and other related&nbsp;dementia care experience with contemporary research developed by leaders in the field.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Every Team Member from housekeeping to administrative services to kitchen staff completes extensive training in the Renaissance Memory Care program to create a consistently safe, respectful, compassionate, and supportive environment.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our primary focus is to create a home-like environment that promotes the resident’s remaining abilities. We collaborate with the resident’s family members to enrich the daily life of&nbsp;Alzheimer''s or dementia residents. This close partnership with family, friends, volunteers and community groups is integral to the well-being of each resident. &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong></strong><strong>Memory, Alzheimer''s &amp; Dementia Care Services Include:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>High Team Member to Resident Ratios</li>\r\n    <li>24 Hour Specially Trained&nbsp;Team Members&nbsp;on Duty</li>\r\n    <li>Medication Management</li>\r\n    <li>Assistance with Activities of Daily Living</li>\r\n    <li>Individualized Care Management Programs</li>\r\n    <li>Balanced, Nutritious Meals Approved by a Nutritionist</li>\r\n    <li>Alzheimer''s and Dementia Family Support and Involvement</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div style="text-align:center;padding:20px 0;border-top:solid 1px #eee;">\r\n	<a href="/assets/docs/EG-Alz-Support-flyer.pdf" target="_blank"><img src="/assets/images/alz-support-group-thumb.jpg" border="0" alt="Alzheimer’s Support Group"/></a>\r\n</div>', 'Memory Care', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '262-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-09-10 19:28:24', '2014-09-10 19:28:24', '', 262, 'http://www.estanciads.com/redesign/262-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(335, 2, '2014-09-10 19:31:41', '2014-09-10 19:31:41', '<h3>Senior care with a difference: a true sense of belonging.</h3>\r\n\r\nBalance is key for a Caregiver: you must replenish your own energy to be strong for those who depend on you day in and day out. Let us care for your family member in a safe, welcoming environment. Rest easy knowing that specially-trained Team Members will surround your loved one with care and respect.\r\n\r\nStay strong. Take care of yourself. Go out to lunch with friends. Shopping for the day. Or take that much-needed vacation. Our respite care Elk Grove program is available hourly, half-day, full-day, overnight or extended respite stays. For fees and additional information, please contact us.\r\n\r\nGive us a call at the number above.', 'Respite Care', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '264-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-09-10 19:31:41', '2014-09-10 19:31:41', '', 264, 'http://www.estanciads.com/redesign/264-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
