(342, 2, '2014-09-10 19:48:27', '2014-09-10 19:48:27', '<h3>Be spoiled. You''ve earned it.</h3>\r\n\r\nWhat should you expect from a place that offers world-class service? Why world-class services of course.\r\n\r\nFrom your weekly housekeeper to the front desk attendant just a phone call away, we are standing by. You''ll be surrounded with people who not only love what they do, but love to serve others. Enjoy inspired meals from our chefs or try a new exercise class. Our concierge awaits your local restaurant, shopping or cultural events requests. And we''re always available to book your manicure, pedicure or hair styling. Or all three.\r\n\r\nTake a look at the full list of WESTclass services in Elk Grove. Because you deserve to be spoiled.', 'Services & Amenities', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '256-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-09-10 19:48:27', '2014-09-10 19:48:27', '', 256, 'http://www.estanciads.com/redesign/256-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(343, 2, '2014-09-10 19:59:38', '2014-09-10 19:59:38', '<h3>Be artistic. Be a green thumb. Be tai chi-ed. Belong.</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>What makes a community a community? The people, of course. Not to mention the barbecues, movie nights, "friendly" card games, gardening sessions, art classes, evening discussions and neighborly support.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With so many daily and weekly activities to choose from, you''re bound to make friends and learn interesting things. Your new community is waiting. Join us.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The following is only a partial list of what we offer:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>Computer Lab and Library</li>\r\n    <li>Happy Hours and Other Social Events</li>\r\n    <li>Landscaped Grounds and Walking Paths</li>\r\n    <li>Weekly Games Schedule</li>\r\n    <li>Arts &amp; Crafts</li>\r\n    <li>Barbecues</li>\r\n    <li>Yoga and Tai Chi</li>\r\n    <li>Guest Lectures and Seminars</li>\r\n    <li>Trips to Local Restaurants, Shopping, and Cultural Events</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Activities', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '268-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-09-10 19:59:38', '2014-09-10 19:59:38', '', 268, 'http://www.estanciads.com/redesign/268-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(344, 2, '2014-09-10 20:13:54', '2014-09-10 20:13:54', '<h3>Welcome to WESTclass service.</h3>\r\n\r\nYou''ve worked hard. Now it''s your turn to sit back and enjoy. Our signature WESTclass service ensures that you''re free from the small tasks that can so quickly eat up the day.\r\n\r\nFrom an attentive front desk to a personal concierge, we''re here to make sure that you don''t just hear the phrase "WESTclass service," you feel it.\r\n\r\nWhat will you do with a personal concierge, you ask? Of course we''re happy to book your next manicure, pedicure or haircut, but we''ll also schedule your four-legged friend''s next dog walk. Want to try that "hot" new restaurant you''ve been hearing about? We''ll make the reservations. Need a gift for your visiting grandchild? We''ll do that and even get it wrapped. Your concierge at independent living in Elk Grove will become so indispensable; you''ll wonder what you did without one until now.\r\n\r\nYes, WESTclass service means your happiness is our happiness, so we''re looking forward to getting to know your smile. From scheduled transportation to dry cleaning to opera tickets, isn''t it nice to know we''ve thought of everything?', 'Concierge', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '272-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-09-10 20:13:54', '2014-09-10 20:13:54', '', 272, 'http://www.estanciads.com/redesign/272-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(346, 2, '2014-09-10 20:24:19', '2014-09-10 20:24:19', '<h3>Variety is the spice of breakfast, lunch and dinner.</h3>\r\n\r\nWhat could be better than sitting down to a delicious meal made with wholesome ingredients? A menu full of tasty choices of course. Here at The Commons at Elk Grove, our chefs prepare a variety of entrees at every meal. So you can get what you''re craving every time. Have a favorite personal recipe? Share it with our staff and we''ll do our best to ensure that it''s offered on the menu.\r\n\r\nOf course, dining options aren''t confined to the menu. Feel free to meet friends in our main restaurant or choose a relaxing meal with you and your family.', 'Dining', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '274-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-09-10 20:24:19', '2014-09-10 20:24:19', '', 274, 'http://www.estanciads.com/redesign/274-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(347, 2, '2014-09-10 20:26:05', '2014-09-10 20:26:05', '<h3>Be coiffed. Be pampered. Be spoiled.</h3>\r\n\r\nWho needs a day of indulgence? You do. Fortunately you need go no further than your own front door to experience salon and spa services, Elk Grove style.\r\n\r\nOur salon and spa menu includes:\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>Haircut</li>\r\n    <li>Hair styling</li>\r\n    <li>Manicure</li>\r\n    <li>Pedicure</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\nEnjoy.', 'Salon & Spa', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '280-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-09-10 20:26:05', '2014-09-10 20:26:05', '', 280, 'http://www.estanciads.com/redesign/280-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(348, 2, '2014-09-10 20:28:26', '2014-09-10 20:28:26', '<h3>Your driver awaits.</h3>\r\n\r\nReady to visit the mall? Take in a concert? Or stop by the grocery store? No worries, even from the front seat, we have your back. Our private and scheduled transportation covers the greater Elk Grove area and we''re ready to take you to your favorite local destination.', 'Transportation', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '282-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-09-10 20:28:26', '2014-09-10 20:28:26', '', 282, 'http://www.estanciads.com/redesign/282-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(349, 2, '2014-09-10 20:34:11', '2014-09-10 20:34:11', '<h3>To know you is to know your favorite kind of smoothie.</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Your well-being is important to us. That''s why we get to know you as a person. Your likes. Your dislikes. Your hobbies. Your individual needs. Even your favorite special recipe or classic movie. In fact, you''ll swear we read your mind as we offer up events, activities and programs tailor-made for you. Crave a morning smoothie? Check. Like to take a mid-day stroll? No problem. Looking forward to watching that new DVD tonight? We thought so.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Wellness Benefits Include:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul class="two-column">\r\n    <li>Daily Exercise and Fitness Programs</li>\r\n    <li>Strengthening and Balance</li>\r\n    <li>Yoga</li>\r\n    <li>Arthritis Foundation Exercise Classes</li>\r\n    <li>Walking Groups</li>\r\n    <li>Equipped Exercise Room</li>\r\n    <li>Social and Intellectual Stimulation</li>\r\n    <li>Educational Seminars</li>\r\n    <li>Religious Worship</li>\r\n    <li>Intergenerational Programs</li>\r\n    <li>Music, Dance, Entertainment and Art</li>\r\n    <li>Brain Fitness Games</li>\r\n    <li>Stimulating Activities</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Health and Well-Being Benefits Include:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul class="two-column">\r\n    <li>Comprehensive Health Assessment</li>\r\n    <li>Pharmacy Consultation Services</li>\r\n    <li>Medication Oversight</li>\r\n    <li>Physical, Occupational Therapy</li>\r\n    <li>Fall Management Program</li>\r\n    <li>Healthy Dining Choices</li>\r\n    <li>Massage and Spa Treatment</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Wellness', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '286-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-09-10 20:34:11', '2014-09-10 20:34:11', '', 286, 'http://www.estanciads.com/redesign/286-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(350, 2, '2014-09-10 20:36:20', '2014-09-10 20:36:20', '<h3>At The Commons at Elk Grove, body and mind are top of mind.</h3>\r\n\r\nEveryone knows that fitness is about improving muscle tone and other aspects of your physical appearance. But did you know that when you engage in physical activity, your brain releases hormones that result in increased energy and happiness?\r\n\r\nIn addition to weights and cardio, we offer programs to improve balance, agility and focus, like yoga and tai chi. Join us. We''ll help you design a total program to keep your heart healthy with exercise as well as proper nutrition and mental well-being.', 'WestFitness', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '278-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-09-10 20:36:20', '2014-09-10 20:36:20', '', 278, 'http://www.estanciads.com/redesign/278-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
