(417, 7, '2014-09-26 23:05:40', '2014-09-26 23:05:40', '<h3>Just because you need a little hand now and then doesn''t mean you can''t still lead.</h3>\r\nAt Estancia Del Sol, assisted living means person-centered care.  Because no two residents'' needs are the same, no two plans are the same.  We''ll help you customize your own care services plan from a full menu of personalized assisted living services.  You decide the options, while we are here to serve.\r\n\r\n<strong>Estancia Del Sol Assisted Living in Corona, Care Options Include:</strong>\r\n<ul class="two-column">\r\n	<li>Medication Supervision</li>\r\n	<li>Medical appointment Scheduling</li>\r\n	<li>Bathing Assistance</li>\r\n	<li>Dressing and Personal Grooming Assistance</li>\r\n	<li>Escort to Meals and Activities</li>\r\n	<li>Ambulation Assistance</li>\r\n	<li>Incontinence Management</li>\r\n	<li>Diabetic Management Assistance</li>\r\n	<li>Special Diets</li>\r\n	<li>Laundry Service</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Amenities Include:</strong>\r\n<ul class="two-column">\r\n	<li>Three Chef-Prepared Meals Daily</li>\r\n	<li>Estancia Restaurant style dining or casual coffee at the Bistro</li>\r\n	<li>Scheduled Transportation</li>\r\n	<li>Health Monitoring</li>\r\n	<li>Apartment Maintenance</li>\r\n	<li>Weekly Housekeeping Services</li>\r\n	<li>All Utilities - Except Telephone - Including Cable TV</li>\r\n	<li>24-Hour Emergency Response</li>\r\n	<li>Comprehensive Activity Program</li>\r\n	<li>Recreational and Social Events</li>\r\n	<li>Exercise and Wellness Programs</li>\r\n	<li>Spacious and state of the art movie theatre</li>\r\n	<li>In-House Pharmacy</li>\r\n	<li>Beauty/Barber Shop</li>\r\n	<li>Private Dining Room</li>\r\n	<li>Guest Meals</li>\r\n	<li>WESTfitness Center</li>\r\n	<li>Landscaped Courtyards</li>\r\n	<li>Pet Friendly Community</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Assisted Living', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '260-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-09-26 23:05:40', '2014-09-26 23:05:40', '', 260, 'http://www.estanciads.com/redesign/260-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(418, 7, '2014-09-26 23:14:42', '2014-09-26 23:14:42', '<h3>This is what senior living was meant to be.</h3>\nYou''ve worked hard. Now it''s time to reap the rewards. And what better place than in a sunny southern California community filled with interesting neighbors, new friends and ever-attentive service?  They may call Corona the circle city, we call it home to a community of interesting opportunities.\n\nAt Estancia Del Sol, community spaces are more than extensions of your home, they''re extensions of your life.  Here, you''ll find the inviting, the comfortable, even the extraordinary.  Our WESTfitness gym will build your body and spirit with cardio and strength training, and improve your agility and focus with yoga or tai chi. After your workout, step outside and enjoy our landscaped grounds and walking path. Or just sit and soak up the sunny southern California sunshine.\n\nOur library and computer lounge area makes it easy to download photos, email, catch up on Facebook, research your next exciting travel adventure or try out our brain fitness program.  After a full day like this, be sure to pamper yourself with a haircut, manicure or pedicure in the salon.\n\nNext, imagine walking into the Estancia Restaurant and seeing your famous homemade spaghetti on the dinner menu.  Or try a cup of coffee and catch up on some local happenings in the Bistro.  We didn''t read your mind, but you''ll feel like we did. Because we take the time to get to know you as a person.  Small, meaningful touches are a way of life around here.\n\nYou could get used to independent living like this in Corona at Estancia Del Sole this.', 'Independent Living', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '258-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-09-26 23:14:42', '2014-09-26 23:14:42', '', 258, 'http://www.estanciads.com/redesign/258-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
