(461, 7, '2014-10-02 22:44:45', '2014-10-02 22:44:45', '<h2>Senior care service for the caregiver and their loved one!</h2>\r\nBalance is key for a caregiver!  Replenishing your own energy to remain strong for those who depend on you day in and day can''t be the last item on the <em>to do</em> list all the time. Let us care for your family member in our safe, welcoming environment. Rest easy knowing that specially-trained Team Members will surround your loved one with care and respect, while you get a chance to take care of yourself.\r\n\r\nYour loved one knows you are strong and always place their needs first. Our respite stay program will allow you to feel guilt-free to take some time for yourself. Go out to lunch with friends. Shopping for the day. Or take that much-needed vacation. The Estancia Del Sol respite care program is available for an convenient overnight stay or for an extended respite stay.  For fees and additional information, please contact us.\r\n\r\nWe''re at your service so you can take care of yourself!', 'Respite Care', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '264-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-10-02 22:44:45', '2014-10-02 22:44:45', '', 264, 'http://www.estanciads.com/redesign/264-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(462, 7, '2014-10-02 23:12:43', '2014-10-02 23:12:43', '<h3>Be artistic. Be a green thumb. Be tai chi-ed.  (Is that a correct term?)  Ah well, be certain to be energized!</h3>\nWhat makes a community a community?  The people, of course!  Not to mention the movie nights, "friendly" card games, gardening sessions, art classes, evening discussions and neighborly support.\n\nSipping a freshly brewed cup of coffee at The Bistro or sitting quietly on one of the many outdoor patios may lead to offers of joining an event something you can''t refuse.  With so many daily and weekly activities to choose from, you''ll definitely make friends while exploring interesting new things.  Come on in and see for yourself.  The opportunities to enjoy are many, but here''s a sample of what you''ll find at Estancia Del Sol.\n<ul>\n	<li>State of the art Computer Lab and Library</li>\n	<li>Happy Hours and Other Social Events at our Estancia Piano Bar</li>\n	<li>Bistro Lounge</li>\n	<li>Maticulously Landscaped Grounds and Walking Paths</li>\n	<li>Grow that rare heirloom tomato in the garden area!</li>\n	<li>Artist Studio</li>\n	<li>Spacious Movie Theatre</li>\n	<li>Yoga and Tai Chi - or just a quick ride on the Biodex!</li>\n	<li>Guest Lectures and Seminars</li>\n	<li>Trips to Local Restaurants, Shopping, and Cultural Events</li>\n</ul>', 'Activities', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '268-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-10-02 23:12:43', '2014-10-02 23:12:43', '', 268, 'http://www.estanciads.com/redesign/268-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
