(484, 7, '2014-10-03 00:02:11', '2014-10-03 00:02:11', '<h3>To know you is to know your favorite kind of smoothie.</h3>\nYour well-being is important to us.  That''s why we get to know you as a person.  Your likes.  Your dislikes.  Your hobbies.  Your individual needs.  Even your favorite special recipe or classic movie.  In fact, you''ll swear we read your mind as we offer up events, activities, and programs tailor-made for you.  Crave a morning smoothie?  Check.  Like to take a mid-day stroll?  No problem.  Looking forward to watching that new DVD tonight?  We thought so.\n\n<strong>Wellness Benefits Include:</strong>\n<ul class="two-column">\n	<li>Daily Exercise and WESTfitness Programs</li>\n	<li>Strengthening and Balance</li>\n	<li>Yoga and Tai Chi Classes</li>\n	<li>Arthritis Foundation Exercise Classes</li>\n	<li>Walking Groups and Silver Sneaker Program</li>\n	<li>WESTfitness GymExercise Room</li>\n	<li>Social and Intellectual Stimulation</li>\n	<li>Educational Seminars</li>\n	<li>Religious Worship</li>\n	<li>Intergenerational Programs</li>\n	<li>Music, Dance, Entertainment and Art</li>\n	<li>Brain Fitness Games</li>\n	<li>Stimulating Activities</li>\n</ul>\n<strong>Health and Well-Being Benefits Include:</strong>\n<ul class="two-column">\n	<li>Comprehensive Health Assessment</li>\n	<li>Pharmacy Consultation Services</li>\n	<li>Medication Oversight</li>\n	<li>Physical, Occupational Therapy</li>\n	<li>Fall Management Program</li>\n	<li>Healthy Dining Choices</li>\n	<li>Massage and Spa Treatment</li>\n</ul>', 'Wellness', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '286-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-10-03 00:02:11', '2014-10-03 00:02:11', '', 286, 'http://www.estanciads.com/redesign/286-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
