(486, 7, '2014-10-03 00:10:21', '2014-10-03 00:10:21', '<h3>Just like WESTclass - WESTfitness at Estancia Del Sol is unique; body and mind are <em>top of mind</em>.</h3>\nEveryone knows that fitness is about improving muscle tone and conditioning other aspects of your physical appearance.  But did you know that when you engage in physical activity, your brain releases hormones that result in increased energy and happiness?\n\nIn addition to weights and cardio, we offer programs to improve balance, agility and focus.  Join us for yoga, tai chi, or a balance exercise to strengthen and put a smile on your face.  We''ll help you design a total program to keep your heart healthy and a comprehensive program to put a little skip to that step!', 'WESTfitness', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '278-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-10-03 00:10:21', '2014-10-03 00:10:21', '', 278, 'http://www.estanciads.com/redesign/278-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
