(504, 2, '2014-11-19 00:10:06', '2014-11-19 00:10:06', '<h2>Experience what senior living was meant to be.</h2>\nYour warm, welcoming place to call home awaits. Call or email us to set up a tour and experience our difference in person.\n\n<h3><strong>McDowell Village</strong>\n8300 East McDowell Road\nScottsdale, AZ 85257\n480-970-6400</h3>\n[widget id="text-17"]\n<div id="p_col1_bottom" class="part_text">\n<h2>Driving Directions</h2>\nFollow these driving directions to reach our senior living community in Scottsdale, AZ.\n<h4>FROM THE SOUTH or NORTH on 101:</h4>\n<ul class="unstyled">\n	<li>Take the 101 to McDowell Road exit (EXIT 49).</li>\n	<li>Travel westbound on McDowell Road.</li>\n	<li>McDowell Village sits on the north side of McDowell Road, just past the Granite.</li>\n	<li>Reef Senior Center, 2 miles west of Hwy 101.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>FROM THE EAST or WEST on either 202 or I60:</h4>\n<ul class="unstyled">\n	<li>Travel West and enter onto the Pima Fwy (101) traveling North.</li>\n	<li>Take the 101 to McDowell Road exit (EXIT 49).</li>\n	<li>Travel westbound on McDowell Road.</li>\n	<li>McDowell Village sits on the north side of McDowell Road, just past the Granite </li>\n	<li></li>\n</ul>\n</div>', 'Maps & Directions', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '20-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-11-19 00:10:06', '2014-11-19 00:10:06', '', 20, 'http://www.estanciads.com/redesign/20-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(505, 2, '2014-10-03 20:48:10', '2014-10-03 20:48:10', '<h3>Experience what senior living was meant to be.</h3>\r\nYour warm, welcoming place to call home awaits. Call or <a href="/redesign/contact/">email us</a> to set up a tour and experience our difference in person.\r\n\r\n<strong>Estancia Del Sol</strong>\r\n2489 California Avenue\r\nCorona, CA  92881\r\n951-340-3200\r\n\r\n[widget id="text-17"]\r\n<div id="p_col1_bottom" class="part_text">\r\n<h2>Driving Directions</h2>\r\nFollow these driving directions to reach our senior living community in Corona, CA.\r\n\r\n<h4>From Highway 15:</h4>\r\n<ul class="unstyled">\r\n	<li>Take the Elk Grove Boulevard exit and go West 0.5 miles.</li>\r\n	<li>Turn right onto Sabrina Lane.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>The Commons at Elk Grove</strong> is located on the corner of Elk Grove Boulevard and Sabrina Lane.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4>From I-5:</h4>\r\n<ul class="unstyled">\r\n	<li>Take the Elk Grove Boulevard exit.</li>\r\n	<li>Go East 4 miles to Laguna Springs Dr.</li>\r\n	<li>Make a U-turn back to Sabrina Lane.</li>\r\n	<li>Arrive at <strong>The Commons at Elk Grove.</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>', 'Maps & Directions', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '20-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-10-03 20:48:10', '2014-10-03 20:48:10', '', 20, 'http://www.estanciads.com/redesign/20-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(506, 7, '2014-10-03 21:29:17', '2014-10-03 21:29:17', '<h3 style="text-align: center;">Corona Senior Living</h3>\r\n<h3 style="text-align: center;">Welcome to world-class service.  Welcome to comfortable, elegant surroundings.  Welcome to what senior living is meant to be in Corona, CA - WESTliving style.</h3>\r\nLooking for a welcoming senior living community with exceptional service in sunny, southern California? You''re right where you belong: <strong>Estancia Del Sol</strong> in Corona, California.\r\n\r\nHere at Estancia Del Sol, we''re dedicated to offering a true sense of belonging to seniors and their families. It''s a feeling you''ll notice the moment you''re invited to "<em>make yourself at home</em>" and continues through every thoughtful, personal detail.\r\n\r\nAs part of the WESTliving family, we understand the importance of world-class service. In fact, we even have a name for it: WESTclass.  It may be a twist on <em>world-class</em> or <em>best in class</em>, but it''s WESTliving culture and inspiration to surprise and delight our customers.  We hire the best Team Members and create an environment that applauds initiative while anticipating the needs of the customer.  The result? Team Members who are empowered to make a meaningful difference in the lives of those we serve.\r\n\r\nFrom independent living, assisted living, and Alzheimer''s or related dementia care in a person-centered environment, our approach reinforces a sense of belonging.  This is achieved by promoting privacy, dignity and a sense of empowerment.  A variety of activities including gardening, art classes, local tours and tai chi await here at Estancia Del Sol.  Just a quick drive from Los Angeles and the Cleveland National Forest.  If a short stay or respite care fits more to your needs, we can customize a plan that meets your personalized desire.\r\n\r\nCome see for yourself how the newest Corona senior living community can become your warm, welcoming place to call home. We''d love to show you around and allow you to experience for yourself a true sense of belonging!  We are here to serve!\r\n\r\n[ssba_hide]', 'Estancia Del Sol', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-10-03 21:29:17', '2014-10-03 21:29:17', '', 2, 'http://www.estanciads.com/redesign/2-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(507, 7, '2014-10-03 21:44:23', '2014-10-03 21:44:23', '<h3>Just because you want a little hand now and then doesn''t mean you can''t still lead.</h3>\r\nAt Estancia Del Sol, we go way beyond traditional assisted living services.  We focus on making it unique to individual wants and desires.  We''ll help you develop your own care services plan from a full menu of personalized assisted living services.  That''s why we have four customizable assisted living levels of service.  You decide the options, while we are here to serve.\r\n\r\n<strong>Estancia Del Sol Assisted Living in Corona, Care Options Include:</strong>\r\n<ul class="two-column">\r\n	<li>Medication Supervision</li>\r\n	<li>Medical appointment Scheduling</li>\r\n	<li>Bathing Assistance</li>\r\n	<li>Dressing and Personal Grooming Assistance</li>\r\n	<li>Escort to Meals and Activities</li>\r\n	<li>Ambulation Assistance</li>\r\n	<li>Incontinence Management</li>\r\n	<li>Diabetic Management Assistance</li>\r\n	<li>Special Diets</li>\r\n	<li>Laundry Service</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Amenities Include:</strong>\r\n<ul class="two-column">\r\n	<li>Three Chef-Prepared Meals Daily</li>\r\n	<li>Estancia Restaurant style dining or casual coffee at The Bistro</li>\r\n	<li>Scheduled Transportation</li>\r\n	<li>Health Monitoring</li>\r\n	<li>Apartment Maintenance</li>\r\n	<li>Weekly Housekeeping Services</li>\r\n	<li>All Utilities - Except Telephone - Including Cable TV</li>\r\n	<li>24-Hour Emergency Response</li>\r\n	<li>Comprehensive Activity Program</li>\r\n	<li>Recreational and Social Events</li>\r\n	<li>Exercise and Wellness Programs</li>\r\n	<li>Spacious and state of the art movie theatre</li>\r\n	<li>In-House Pharmacy</li>\r\n	<li>Beauty/Barber Shop</li>\r\n	<li>Private Dining Room</li>\r\n	<li>Guest Meals</li>\r\n	<li>WESTfitness Center</li>\r\n	<li>Landscaped Courtyards</li>\r\n	<li>Pet Friendly Community</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Assisted Living', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '260-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-10-03 21:44:23', '2014-10-03 21:44:23', '', 260, 'http://www.estanciads.com/redesign/260-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(508, 7, '2014-10-03 21:48:04', '2014-10-03 21:48:04', '<h2>Senior care service for the caregiver and their loved one!</h2>\r\nBalance is key for a caregiver!  Replenishing your own energy to remain strong for those who depend on you day in and day can''t be the last item on the <em>to do</em> list all the time. Let us care for your family member in our safe, welcoming environment. Rest easy knowing that specially-trained Team Members will surround your loved one with care and respect, while you get a chance to take care of yourself.\r\n\r\nYour loved one knows you are strong and always place their needs first. Our respite stay program will allow you to feel guilt-free to take some time for yourself. Go out to lunch with friends. Shopping for the day. Or take that much-needed vacation. The Estancia Del Sol respite care program is available for a convenient overnight stay or for an extended respite stay.  For fees and additional information, please contact us.\r\n\r\nWe''re at your service so you can take care of yourself!', 'Respite Care', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '264-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-10-03 21:48:04', '2014-10-03 21:48:04', '', 264, 'http://www.estanciads.com/redesign/264-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(510, 7, '2014-10-03 22:26:05', '2014-10-03 22:26:05', '<h3><strong>Estancia Del Sol</strong>\r\n2489 California Avenue\r\nCorona, CA  92881\r\n951-340-3200</h3>\r\n[widget id="text-17"]\r\n<div id="p_col1_bottom" class="part_text">\r\n<h2>Driving Directions</h2>\r\nFollow these driving directions to reach our senior living community in Corona, CA.\r\n<h4>Directions from North:</h4>\r\n<ul class="unstyled">\r\n	<li>Depart CA-91 W and take ramp right for I-15 South towards San Diego</li>\r\n	<li>Take exit 93, Ontario Avenue</li>\r\n	<li>Turn right onto Ontario Avenue</li>\r\n	<li>Turn left onto California Avenue (KFC on the corner)</li>\r\n	<li>Just past the first light, Estancia Del Sol''s entrance is on your left</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4>Directions from South:</h4>\r\n<ul class="unstyled">\r\n	<li>Take I-15 N to exit 93, Ontario Avenue</li>\r\n	<li>Turn left onto Ontario Avenue</li>\r\n	<li>Turn left onto California Avenue (KFC on the corner)</li>\r\n	<li>Just past the first light, Estancia Del Sol''s entrance is on your left</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>', 'Maps & Directions', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '20-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-10-03 22:26:05', '2014-10-03 22:26:05', '', 20, 'http://www.estanciads.com/redesign/20-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
