(512, 2, '2014-10-06 16:35:28', '2014-10-06 16:35:28', '<p class="intro-text">Isn''t it time you spent time with people as interesting as you?</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Be yourself. You''re right where you belong.</h3>\r\nHe says tomato. She says tomahto. And that''s exactly what makes things interesting around here. By embracing everyone''s uniqueness, we''ve created a community where everyone feels like they belong. That''s why here at Estancia Del Sol, you can choose the senior living lifestyle option that fits you. Choose from Estancia Del Sol senior living options including independent living, living that offers assistance with your everyday routine, Alzheimer''s and dementia care or respite care. Plus our wide range of amenities and activities means there''s always something to inspire, excite, relax or intrigue. Why let another day go by without learning tai chi? Without taking up watercolors? Without strolling the garden? Don''t worry, we have the details covered. All you have to do is enjoy.', 'Living Options', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '10-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-10-06 16:35:28', '2014-10-06 16:35:28', '', 10, 'http://www.estanciads.com/redesign/10-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(513, 2, '2014-10-06 16:37:41', '2014-10-06 16:37:41', '<p class="intro-text">Isn''t it time you spent time with people as interesting as you?</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Be yourself. You''re right where you belong.</h3>\r\nHe says tomato. She says tomahto. And that''s exactly what makes things interesting around here. By embracing everyone''s uniqueness, we''ve created a retirement community where everyone feels like they belong. That''s why here at Estancia Del Sol, you can choose the senior living lifestyle option that fits you. Choose from Estancia Del Sol senior living options including independent living, living that offers assistance with your everyday routine, Alzheimer''s and dementia care or respite care. Plus our wide range of amenities and activities means there''s always something to inspire, excite, relax or intrigue. Why let another day go by without learning tai chi? Without taking up watercolors? Without strolling the garden? Don''t worry, we have the details covered. All you have to do is enjoy.', 'Living Options', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '10-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-10-06 16:37:41', '2014-10-06 16:37:41', '', 10, 'http://www.estanciads.com/redesign/10-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(514, 2, '2014-11-05 23:24:37', '2014-11-05 23:24:37', '<div class="row">\n    <div class="col-sm-3"><img class="margin-top-10" src="/wp-content/uploads/sam-faye.jpg" alt="Sam Faye" /></div>\n    <div class="col-sm-9">\n        <h2>Sam Faye</h2>\n        <h4>General Manager</h4>\n        As our General Manager, Sam Faye brings senior housing hospitality leadership to a new level at Estancia Del Sol.  With over 20 years of diverse experience from both the senior housing and hospitality industries, Sam leads our team of service professionals.  Sam’s award-winning background includes pioneer work in establishing market awareness with successful openings of new senior housing communities in California.  His customer engagement, organizational skills, and attention to detail sets the bar high through a team approach to service delivery.  Sam developed his hospitality roots in many well-known lodging organizations, acting as the catalyst to apply his hospitality expertise to an older adult customer in early 2000.  He is a hands-on leader in supporting his team, while fostering operational plans for success.  Sam prides himself on building exceptional teams and delivering legendary service.  Couple this with his genuine sense of humor and quick wit to put anyone at ease, and we are confident you’ll experience memorable moments at Estancia Del Sol.\n    </div>\n</div>\n<div class="row">\n    <div class="col-sm-3"><img class="margin-top-10" src="/wp-content/uploads/carrie-compton.jpg" alt="Carrie Compton" /></div>\n    <div class="col-sm-9">\n        <h2>Carrie Compton</h2>\n        <h4>Sales Director</h4>\n        When you meet Carrie Compton, our Sales Director, you’ll quickly realize that she demonstrates genuine interest and compassion for serving older adults.  She not only is a wonderful listener, she is attentive in understanding unique desires and interests of others.  Her many years in senior housing sales draw upon the exploratory, the unique, the passions of others – creating solutions and options the customer can experience as a customized housing and amenities match distinct to them.  Carrie provides the right level of service to ultimately find that special place older adults can call home.  You can personally experience this for yourself – so come on in so she can show you around!  She welcomes the chance to spend some time with you and see how Estancia Del Sol can fulfill your desires and create the unexpected.\n    </div>\n</div>\n<div class="row">\n    <div class="col-sm-3"><img class="margin-top-10" src="/wp-content/uploads/stephen-pratt.jpg" alt="Stephen Pratt" /></div>\n    <div class="col-sm-9">\n        <h2>Stephen Pratt</h2>\n        <h4>Marketing Liaison</h4>\n        Stephen’s goal as Marketing Liaison is bringing our amenities and services to light in the greater market of Corona and the surrounding area.  Stephen works closely with Carrie in sales through education about our community, relationship building with referral sources, and educating all who are willing to hear about what Estancia Del Sol is all about.  Stephen draws upon two areas to get the word out about Estancia Del Sol: Through his many roles in growing up in the business in other senior housing communities, as well as his sincere interest to educate older adults and professionals working with seniors in truly understanding how Estancia Del Sol offers opportunities to enjoy a better quality of life.  You may have encountered Stephen through a presentation to a group or through an introduction by your health care professional.  Either way, he sees the best part of his role was accomplished with a better understanding of how we can help!\n    </div>\n</div>\n<div class="row">\n    <div class="col-sm-3"><img class="margin-top-10" src="/wp-content/uploads/allen-johnson.jpg" alt="Allen Johnson" /></div>\n    <div class="col-sm-9">\n        <h2>Allen Johnson</h2>\n        <h4>Food & Beverage Director</h4>\n        <p>Allen would describe his role in humble terms, but that would not do justice to his culinary direction and expertise as our Food & Beverage Director.  Think of the creative, gourmet, an elegant dining experience!  We take pride in Allen’s ability to create your memorable dining experience with his team of dining professionals through his impressive resume, including:</p>\n        <ul>\n            <li>Culinary Arts degree - The Culinary Arts Institute of America, NY</li>\n            <li>International Chef with focus on French Pastries – Ecole Superieure Cuisine de Francaise Ferrandi, Paris, France</li>\n            <li>Opening over 20 restaurants domestically and internationally</li>\n            <li>Voted Top 3 Breakfast Spot Restaurants by Trillst and commended by Travel and Leisure, Lockwood, Paris 2013</li>\n        </ul>\n        <p>Once you experience for yourself, you’ll see how his proof is in the pudding as well as in his craft.  Best of all, he may share more personal insights to his time cooking at the 1996 Olympic Games in Atlanta or for the 6,000+ Marines and Army servicemen in Kuwait.</p>\n    </div>\n</div>', 'Meet Our Team', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '22-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-11-05 23:24:37', '2014-11-05 23:24:37', '', 22, 'http://www.estanciads.com/redesign/22-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(515, 2, '2014-10-07 23:15:00', '2014-10-07 23:15:00', '<div class="media">\r\n    <div class="media-body">\r\n        <h2 class="media-heading">Sam Faye</h2>\r\n        <h4>General Manager</h4>\r\n        Bringing with him over 20 years of diverse experience from both the Senior Housing and\r\n        Hospitality industries, Sam Faye is delighted to part of the WESTliving team as General Manager for Estancia Del Sol.\r\n        \r\n        Sam has been a successful, award-winning Senior Housing professional for almost 12 years. His management background of all facets of Senior Housing includes Independent Living, Assisted Living, Memory Care and Continuing Care Retirement Communities. Sam prides himself on building exceptional teams, delivering legendary service and creating memorable experiences that delight residents.\r\n        \r\n        As an Executive Director for the past decade, Mr. Faye also became known as the man to call on to successfully open upscale new senior communities with companies such as Aegis and Oakmont Senior Living. Prior to his career in Senior Housing, Sam enjoyed a career in the hospitality industry that took him to the Florida Keys, the Navajo Indian reservation, and up and down the west coast with companies such as Hilton, Embassy Suites and Holiday Inn.\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="media">\r\n    <div class="media-body">\r\n        <h2 class="media-heading">Carrie Compton</h2>\r\n        <h4>Sales Director</h4>\r\n        Twelve years ago, Carrie began her career in sales and marketing in the senior living industry. When asked what she loves most about this line of work she said, “Being able to make such a huge and meaningful difference in the lives of seniors and their families and to watch them smile, laugh and be loved by a caring staff.  Moving to a Retirement\r\n        Community for most seniors can be scary and a change they wish they didn’t have to make. But it gives me such pleasure to see how happy they become once they do make the move.”\r\n        \r\n        After 12 years and three communities later, Carrie is beyond happy and grateful to be given the position here at   Estancia Del Sol. Being able to be a part of a flagship community for WESTliving is a dream come true.\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="media">\r\n    <div class="media-body">\r\n        <h2 class="media-heading">Stephen Pratt</h2>\r\n        <h4>Marketing Liaison</h4>\r\n        Stephen brings eight years of experience in Senior Housing to his position as Marketing Liaison. His journey in Senior Living began back in 2006. His multifaceted experience includes Server, Caregiver, Medication Tech, Concierge, Activities Coordinator, Administrative Assistant and Sales Counselor. Stephen states, “I became so attached to the residents after working in senior living for the last few years, it has become a passion — so much so that I don’t ever want to leave this industry! \r\n        \r\n        Work is not ‘work’ for me, because I get to do something I love doing and I’m able to share my life and accomplishments with, what seem like, adopted grandparents. It is a bond that is so hard to explain without being a part of it.”   After graduating from California State University - Fullerton, Stephen began a position as a senior living Sales Counselor. One year later, WESTliving chose Stephen as their Marketing Liaison. “The best part about my job now  is getting to hear the stories of each individual who walks through the door, and it is so gratifying being able to help people in their search for a better quality of life.”\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>', 'Meet Our Team', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '22-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-10-07 23:15:00', '2014-10-07 23:15:00', '', 22, 'http://www.estanciads.com/redesign/22-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
