(614, 2, '2014-10-27 23:33:43', '2014-10-27 23:33:43', 'Less than a year ago construction of Estancia Del Sol broke ground. Now instead of wooden frames and dirt, the community and landscape are taking shape. Interior walls are in place, windows have been installed and the stone finishes are close to completion throughout the property.\r\n\r\nThe Marketing team and General Manager are thrilled with the tremendous interest in their community. Future residents are already beginning to pick out their preferred units. Carrie Compton, Sales Director, stated, “This property is state of the art, and will give a true sense of belonging – making you feel right at home. We will have phenomenal programing to keep our residents engaged and healthy!”\r\n\r\nStarting at just $2,650 a month, residents enjoy three restaurant style meals, high-end amenities and WESTclass hospitality every day. Come visit the leasing center and find out more of what Estancia Del Sol will have to offer!\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<div class="col-md-3">\r\n<a href="http://www.estanciads.com/wp-content/uploads/construction-update-91014-1.jpg" rel="lightbox" alt="" title=""><img src="http://www.estanciads.com/redesign/wp-content/uploads/construction-update-thumb-1.jpg" alt="construction-update-thumb-1" width="176" height="176" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-557" alt="" title="" /></a>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-3">\r\n<a href="http://www.estanciads.com/wp-content/uploads/construction-update-91014-2.jpg" rel="lightbox" alt="" title=""><img src="http://www.estanciads.com/redesign/wp-content/uploads/construction-update-thumb-2.jpg" alt="construction-update-thumb-2" width="176" height="176" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-558" alt="" title="" /></a>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-3">\r\n<a href="http://www.estanciads.com/wp-content/uploads/construction-update-91014-3.jpg" rel="lightbox" alt="" title=""><img src="http://www.estanciads.com/redesign/wp-content/uploads/construction-update-thumb-3.jpg"