(582, 2, '2014-10-15 21:36:41', '2014-10-15 21:36:41', '<h3>Variety is the spice of breakfast, lunch and dinner - Estancia Del Sol Style</h3>\r\nWhat could be better than sitting down to a delicious meal made with fresh wholesome ingredients and farm-to-table produce? A menu full of tasty choices and flavors that excite the palate.  You''ll taste many flavorful options at our Estancia Restaurant, as our chefs prepare a variety of entrees at every meal.  So you can get what you''re craving every time.  Have a favorite personal recipe?  Share it with our Food &amp; Beverage Director and we''ll do our best to ensure that it''s offered on the menu.\r\n\r\nOf course, dining options aren''t confined to the menu or location.  Feel free to meet friends in our Estancia Restaurant or choose a continental option at The Bistro.  Just like our service offerings, you pick and we''ll create to provide the relaxing meal with you and your family.', 'Restaurant Dining or Casual Bistro', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '274-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-10-15 21:36:41', '2014-10-15 21:36:41', '', 274, 'http://www.estanciads.com/redesign/274-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(583, 2, '2014-10-15 21:54:15', '2014-10-15 21:54:15', '<h3>This is what independent senior living was meant to be.</h3>\nYou''ve worked hard. Now it''s time to reap the rewards. And what better place than in a sunny southern California community filled with interesting neighbors, new friends and ever-attentive service?  They may call Corona the circle city, we call it home to a community of interesting opportunities.\n\nAt Estancia Del Sol, community spaces are more than extensions of your home, they''re extensions of your life.  Here, you''ll find the inviting, the comfortable, even the extraordinary.  Our WESTfitness gym will build your body and spirit with cardio and strength training, and improve your agility and focus with yoga or tai chi. After your workout, step outside and enjoy our landscaped grounds and walking path. Or just sit and soak up the sunny southern California sunshine.\n\nOur library and computer lounge area makes it easy to download photos, email, catch up on Facebook, research your next exciting travel adventure or try out our brain fitness program.  After a full day like this, be sure to pamper yourself with a haircut, manicure or pedicure in the salon.\n\nNext, imagine walking into the Estancia Restaurant and seeing your famous homemade spaghetti on the dinner menu.  Or try a cup of coffee and catch up on some local happenings in the Bistro.  We didn''t read your mind, but you''ll feel like we did. Because we take the time to get to know you as a person.  Small, meaningful touches are a way of life around here.\n\nYou could get used to independent living like this in Corona, at <strong>Estancia Del Sol</strong>.', 'Independent Living', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '258-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-10-15 21:54:15', '2014-10-15 21:54:15', '', 258, 'http://www.estanciads.com/redesign/258-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
