(596, 2, '2014-10-16 20:44:40', '2014-10-16 20:44:40', '<h3>Be artistic. Be a green thumb. Be tai chi-ed. (Is that a correct term?) Ah well, be certain to be energized!</h3>\nWhat makes a community a community?  The people, of course!  Not to mention the movie nights, "friendly" card games, gardening sessions, art classes, evening discussions and neighborly support.\n\nSipping a freshly brewed cup of coffee at The Bistro or sitting quietly on one of the many outdoor patios may lead to offers of joining an event something you can''t refuse.  With so many daily and weekly community activities to choose from, you''ll definitely make friends while exploring interesting new things.  Come on in and see for yourself.  The opportunities to enjoy are many, but here''s a sample of what you''ll find at Estancia Del Sol.\n<ul>\n	<li>State of the art Computer Lab and Library</li>\n	<li>Happy Hours and Other Social Events at our Estancia Piano Bar</li>\n	<li>Bistro Lounge</li>\n	<li>Maticulously Landscaped Grounds and Walking Paths</li>\n	<li>Grow that rare heirloom tomato in the garden area!</li>\n	<li>Artist Studio</li>\n	<li>Spacious Movie Theatre</li>\n	<li>WESTfitness Yoga and Tai Chi - or just a quick ride on the Biodex!</li>\n	<li>Guest Lectures and Seminars</li>\n	<li>Trips to Local Restaurants, Shopping, and Cultural Events</li>\n</ul>', 'Retirement Community Activities', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '268-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-10-16 20:44:40', '2014-10-16 20:44:40', '', 268, 'http://www.estanciads.com/redesign/268-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
