(600, 2, '2014-10-16 20:51:18', '2014-10-16 20:51:18', '<h3>Welcome to WESTclass service.</h3>\nYou''ve worked hard.  Now it''s your turn to sit back and enjoy!  Our signature WESTclass service''s senior living concierge is here to surprise and delight, while delivering on the unexpected.  That may seem unrealistic, but our culture thrives on it.\n\nFrom that first greeting to the moment you meet the personal concierge, we''re here to make sure that you don''t just hear the phrase "How can I serve you - WESTclass?," you''ll sense our genuine desire to serve in each Team Member you encounter.  Our Hospitality Director is at your service with her team of professionals as your personal concierge.\n\nWhat will you do with a personal concierge, you ask?  Of course we''re happy to book your next manicure, pedicure or haircut, but we''ll also schedule your four-legged friend''s next dog walk.  Want to try that "hot" new restaurant you''ve been hearing about?  We''ll make the reservations.  Need a gift for your visiting grandchild?  We''ll make it happen and even get it wrapped.  Senior Living in Corona with an attentive concierge service will become so indispensable, you''ll wonder what you did without one until now.\n\nYes, WESTclass service means we''ll do what it takes to anticipate and delight, while enjoying the outcome in seeing your smile.', 'Concierge', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '272-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-10-16 20:51:18', '2014-10-16 20:51:18', '', 272, 'http://www.estanciads.com/redesign/272-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
