(602, 2, '2014-10-16 21:02:26', '2014-10-16 21:02:26', '<h3>Variety is the spice of breakfast, lunch and dinner - Estancia Del Sol Style</h3>\r\nRetirement community dining at its best. What could be better than sitting down to a delicious meal made with fresh wholesome ingredients and farm-to-table produce? A menu full of tasty choices and flavors that excite the palate.  You''ll taste many flavorful options at our Estancia Restaurant, as our chefs prepare a variety of entrees at every meal.  So you can get what you''re craving every time.  Have a favorite personal recipe?  Share it with our Food &amp; Beverage Director and we''ll do our best to ensure that it''s offered on the menu.\r\n\r\nOf course, dining options aren''t confined to the menu or location.  Feel free to meet friends in our Estancia Restaurant or choose a continental option at The Bistro.  Just like our service offerings, you pick and we''ll create to provide the relaxing meal with you and your family.', 'Restaurant Dining or Casual Bistro', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '274-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-10-16 21:02:26', '2014-10-16 21:02:26', '', 274, 'http://www.estanciads.com/redesign/274-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(603, 2, '2014-10-16 21:11:19', '2014-10-16 21:11:19', '<h3>To know you is to know your favorite kind of smoothie.</h3>\nSenior wellness and your well-being is important to us.  That''s why we get to know you as a person.  Your likes.  Your dislikes.  Your hobbies.  Your individual needs.  Even your favorite special recipe or classic movie.  In fact, you''ll swear we read your mind as we offer up events, activities, and programs tailor-made for you.  Crave a morning smoothie?  Check.  Like to take a mid-day stroll?  No problem.  Looking forward to watching that new DVD tonight?  We thought so.\n\n<strong>Senior Wellness Benefits Include:</strong>\n<ul class="two-column">\n	<li>Daily Exercise and WESTfitness Programs</li>\n	<li>Strengthening and Balance</li>\n	<li>Yoga and Tai Chi Classes</li>\n	<li>Arthritis Foundation Exercise Classes</li>\n	<li>Walking Groups and Silver Sneaker Program</li>\n	<li>WESTfitness Gym</li>\n	<li>Social and Intellectual Stimulation</li>\n	<li>Educational Seminars</li>\n	<li>Religious Worship</li>\n	<li>Intergenerational Programs</li>\n	<li>Music, Dance, Entertainment and Art</li>\n	<li>Brain Fitness Games</li>\n	<li>Stimulating Activities</li>\n</ul>\n<strong>Health and Well-Being Benefits Include:</strong>\n<ul class="two-column">\n	<li>Comprehensive Health Assessment</li>\n	<li>Pharmacy Consultation Services</li>\n	<li>Medication Oversight</li>\n	<li>Physical, Occupational Therapy</li>\n	<li>Fall Management Program</li>\n	<li>Healthy Dining Choices</li>\n	<li>Massage and Spa Treatment</li>\n</ul>', 'Senior Wellness', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '286-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-10-16 21:11:19', '2014-10-16 21:11:19', '', 286, 'http://www.estanciads.com/redesign/286-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
