(789, 8, '2014-11-25 23:19:51', '2014-11-25 23:19:51', '<h3>Your driver awaits.</h3>\nReady to visit the mall? Take in a concert? Or stop by the grocery store? No worries, even from the front seat, we have your back. Our private and scheduled transportation covers the greater Scottsdale area and we''re ready to take you to any local destination.', 'Transportation', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '282-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-11-25 23:19:51', '2014-11-25 23:19:51', '', 282, 'http://dev.mcdowellvillage.com/blog/282-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
