(791, 8, '2014-11-25 23:23:20', '2014-11-25 23:23:20', '<h3>At McDowell Village, body and mind are top of mind.</h3>\r\nEveryone knows that fitness is about improving muscle tone and other aspects of your physical appearance. But it also involves keeping your heart healthy with proper nutrition, and enhancing your mental and spiritual well-being through inner work. When you engage in physical activity, your brain releases hormones that result in increased energy and happiness.\r\n\r\nIn addition to weights and cardio, we offer programs to improve balance, agility and focus, like yoga and tai chi. If you love spending time in the pool, join us for an instructor-led aquatics class. Relax in the jacuzzi, then enjoy a muscle-soothing massage. You''ve earned it.', 'WESTfitness', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '278-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-11-25 23:23:20', '2014-11-25 23:23:20', '', 278, 'http://dev.mcdowellvillage.com/blog/278-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(792, 8, '2014-11-25 23:24:27', '2014-11-25 23:24:27', '<h3>Your go-to guide for all of our goings-on.</h3>\r\nQuick. Before you read any further, bookmark this page. Because this is your go-to guide for all things McDowell Village. Here, you''ll find the most up-to-date information on in-house activities, outings, special events and other daily programming for residents of our community.\r\n\r\nActivities include everything from shopping excursions and museum trips to yoga and aquatics classes to movie nights and ice cream socials. Check back soon to see what exciting new adventures we''ve added.\r\n\r\n<strong>Proud Winner of the 2012 Sterling Awards - Small Business</strong>\r\n\r\nMcDowell Village has been named the winner of the 26th annual Sterling Awards. Conducted by the Scottsdale Area Chamber of Commerce, this marquee event celebrates business excellence in our greater Scottsdale Valley community. One of the most coveted business awards in the area, the Sterling Awards judging committee selected McDowell Village as the winner over 30 other prestigious competitors after a rigorous application, judging and selection process.', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '12-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-11-25 23:24:27', '2014-11-25 23:24:27', '', 12, 'http://dev.mcdowellvillage.com/blog/12-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(714, 2, '2014-11-19 18:47:33', '2014-11-19 18:47:33', '<h3>Your new neighbors are eager to tell you about McDowell Village.</h3>\r\n\r\n<div class="row testimonials-items">\r\n	<div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 testimonials-item">\r\n    	<span class="ti-quote">Our home is a wonderful place to live...I feel very lucky to have the staff making it so fine!!! I love the Village!</span>\r\n        <span class="ti-name">Leah W.</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n	<div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 testimonials-item">\r\n    	<span class="ti-quote">Thank you for caring for my mother so much!</span>\r\n        <span class="ti-name">Tom & Marge D.</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row testimonials-items">\r\n	<div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 testimonials-item">\r\n    	<span class="ti-quote">I can never put into words how grateful I am for everything you have done for our family.</span>\r\n        <span class="ti-name">Lois S.</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n	<div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 testimonials-item">\r\n    	<span class="ti-quote">I plan to live here forever.</span>\r\n        <span class="ti-name">Bev M.</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row testimonials-items">\r\n	<div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 testimonials-item">\r\n    	<span class="ti-quote">Thank you for helping with selection of movers, making a place for my piano, my two day stay, always answering my calls and your patience in going over the many details of the move.</span>\r\n        <span class="ti-name">Vera M.</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n	<div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 testimonials-item">\r\n    	<span class="ti-quote">This is the best decision I have ever made (moving to McDowell Village). I should have done this two years ago!</span>\r\n        <span class="ti-name">Lilo K.</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row testimonials-items">\r\n	<div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 testimonials-item">\r\n    	<span class="ti-quote">Love it here</span>\r\n        <span class="ti-name">Marian O.</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n	<div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 testimonials-item">\r\n    	<span class="ti-quote">The living areas, bathrooms and hallways are so impeccably clean each time we visit.</span>\r\n        <span class="ti-name">Resident daughter</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row testimonials-items">\r\n	<div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 testimonials-item">\r\n    	<span class="ti-quote">I have enjoyed living here and hope that God will grant me many more years to enjoy the ambiance of the Village.</span>\r\n        <span class="ti-name">Lee D.</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n	<div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 testimonials-item">\r\n    	<span class="ti-quote">When Hazel said she wanted to go home, she didn''t mean her house of 50+ years - it was to her apartment at McDowell Village. Her time there was some of the happiest of her life.</span>\r\n        <span class="ti-name">Resident daughter</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row testimonials-items">\r\n	<div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 testimonials-item">\r\n    	<span class="ti-quote">I am more at peace, being nearly 3000 miles away, knowing you oversee my parents at McDowell Village. The attention to detail is unsurpassed.</span>\r\n        <span class="ti-name">Resident daughter</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n	<div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 testimonials-item">\r\n    	<span class="ti-quote">I am always amazed, when we have a festival day, at how hard you all work to make sure everything falls in place - just so.</span>\r\n        <span class="ti-name">Olive S.</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row testimonials-items">\r\n	<div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 testimonials-item">\r\n    	<span class="ti-quote">Thank you for advocating independence, decision-making, and freedom for the Seniors at McDowell.</span>\r\n        <span class="ti-name">Kathy M.</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n	<div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 testimonials-item">\r\n    	<span class="ti-quote">I can''t tell you how much it means to know that when something happens to my mother, there are people right there that rally to her aid.</span>\r\n        <span class="ti-name">Anne R.</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row testimonials-items">\r\n	<div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 testimonials-item">\r\n    	<span class="ti-quote">If you want to know what happened to me: I''ve died and gone to heaven!!!</span>\r\n        <span class="ti-name">Janet H.</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>', 'Testimonials', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '252-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-11-19 18:47:33', '2014-11-19 18:47:33', '', 252, 'http://dev.mcdowellvillage.com/252-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
