(716, 8, '2014-11-19 21:23:25', '2014-11-19 21:23:25', '<h2>Scottsdale Senior Living</h2>\r\n<h3>Welcome to world-class service. Welcome to comfortable, elegant surroundings. Welcome to senior living in Scottsdale, WESTliving style.</h3>\r\nLooking for perfect weather in beautiful surroundings at a welcoming community with exceptional service? You''re right where you belong: McDowell Village in Scottsdale, Arizona.\r\n\r\nHere at McDowell Village, we''re dedicated to offering a true sense of belonging to seniors and their families. It''s a feeling you''ll notice the moment you''re invited to "make yourself at home" and continues through every thoughtful, personal detail.\r\n\r\nAs part of the WESTliving family, we understand the importance of world-class service. In fact, we even have a name for it: WESTclass service. We hire carefully and train extensively. The result? Team Members who are empowered to make a meaningful difference in the lives of those we serve and inspired to anticipate your next need – before you even know you have a next need.\r\n\r\nFrom physical and intellectual well-being to emotional and spiritual health, we take the time to know you as a person. Maybe your passion is fitness. May we suggest afternoon tai chi? Or perhaps you''d prefer to relax at our in-house spa or share a quiet desert sunset with a friend.\r\n\r\nYour warm, welcoming place to call home awaits at our Scottsdale senior living community. Call the number above or <a href="http://www.mcdowellvillage.com/leads/email_us/index.php">email us</a> to set up a tour and experience our difference in person.\r\n\r\n[ssba_hide]', 'McDowell Village', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-11-19 21:23:25', '2014-11-19 21:23:25', '', 2, 'http://dev.mcdowellvillage.com/2-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(718, 8, '2014-11-19 21:28:49', '2014-11-19 21:28:49', 'SCOTTSDALE SENIOR LIVING OPTIONS\n\n<p class="intro-text">Isn''t it time you spent time with people as interesting as you?</p>\n\n<h3>Be yourself. You''re right where you belong.</h3>\nHe says tomato. She says tomahto. And that''s exactly what makes things interesting around here. By embracing everyone''s uniqueness, we''ve created a community where everyone feels like they belong. That''s why here at McDowell Village, you can choose from Scottsdale senior care options including senior living, living that offers assistance with your everyday routine or respite care. Plus our wide range of amenities and adventures means there''s always something to inspire, excite, relax or intrigue. Why let another day go by without learning the Argentine tango? Without taking up watercolors? Without seeing Maui? Don''t worry, we have the details covered. All you have to do is enjoy.', 'Living Options', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '10-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-11-19 21:28:49', '2014-11-19 21:28:49', '', 10, 'http://dev.mcdowellvillage.com/10-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(720, 8, '2014-11-19 21:20:31', '2014-11-19 21:20:31', 'INDEPENDENT LIVING, SCOTTSDALE STYLE.\r\n\r\n<h3>This is what independent living was meant to be.</h3>\r\nYou''ve worked hard. Now it''s time to reap the rewards. And what better place than in a beautiful Scottsdale community filled with interesting neighbors, new friends and ever-attentive service? \r\n\r\nAt McDowell Village, community spaces are more than extensions of your home, they''re extensions of your life. Here, you''ll find the inviting, the comfortable, even the extraordinary. Our state-of-the art gym will build your body and spirit with cardio and strength training, yoga, tai chi and other alternative programs. After your workout, step outside for a relaxing soak in the jacuzzi or lounge by the pool with friends. Still full of energy? Feel free to join an instructor-led aquatics class.\r\n\r\nOur computer lounge makes it easy to download photos, email, catch up on Facebook, research your next exciting travel adventure or try out our brain fitness program. After a full day like this, be sure to pamper yourself with a manicure or pedicure in the salon.\r\n\r\nNext, imagine walking into the dining room and seeing your famous homemade spaghetti on the dinner menu. Or sitting down in the in-house movie theater as your very favorite movie begins to play. We didn''t read your mind, but you''ll feel like we did. Because we take the time to get to know you as a person. Small, meaningful touches are a way of life around here.\r\n\r\n*Independent Living at <strong>McDowell Village</strong> in Scottsdale. You could get used to this.*\r\n', 'Independent Living', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '258-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-11-19 21:20:31', '2014-11-19 21:20:31', '', 258, 'http://dev.mcdowellvillage.com/258-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
