(735, 2, '2014-11-20 19:27:16', '2014-11-20 19:27:16', '<h3>About the "All Things Senior" Expo & Tradeshow</h3>\r\n\r\nEvery year in February, Scottsdale Senior Services brings together an extensive collection of exhibitors who provide products, resources and valuable services to the 50+ community.  If you are looking for information about healthcare, senior housing, municipal services, recreation, technology, transportation or entertainment, the "All Things Senior" Expo & Tradeshow will provide lasting connections to help enhance your quality of life. \r\n\r\nIn addition to a wide vareity of resources, the event features free health screenings, educational opportunities and live entertainment.  Be on the lookout for a full event agenda in January.\r\n\r\n<h3>Exhibitors</h3>\r\n\r\nScottsdale is widely recognized as a premier community for retirees and senior adults.  Close to 40% of Scottsdale''s residents are 50 plus and Scottsdale contains the largest percentage of citizens who are 65 plus in the United States (for cities with a population over 100,000).  Furthermore, the "Baby Boomers" will increase our community''s 65+ population by over 50% by 2020.  Any way you look at it, older adults are an incredible market for retail providers, healthcare and anyone providing services.\r\n\r\nOver 3,000 people attended last year''s event, making it a spectacular avenue to showcase products, services or programs.  If you are a business that is looking to connect with a high volume of local seniors, the "All Things Senior" Expo & Tradeshow is for you!\r\n\r\nAre you interested in becoming an exhibitor at the 2015 "All Things Senior" Expo &amp; Tradeshow? The 2015 exhibitor application is now available. If you have questions or need additional information, contact Susie Cummings at <a href="mailto:scummings@scottsdaleaz.gov">scummings@scottsdaleaz.gov</a> or 480-312-5811.\r\n\r\n<a href="/Assets/Public+Website/seniors/2015+All+Things+Senior+Expo+$!26+Tradeshow+Exhibitor+Application.pdf" title="2015 Senior Expo Exhibitor Application">2015 All Things Senior Expo &amp; Tradeshow Exhibitor Application</a>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>To keep up-to-date about events and activities with Scottsdale Senior Services, "like" our <a href="http://www.Facebook.com/ScottsdaleSeniors" title="Senior Services Facebook Page">Facebook page</a> and sign up for our <a href="https://eservices.scottsdaleaz.gov/ListServe" title="Email Subscription">email subscription</a></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Exhibitor Testimonials</h3>\r\n\r\n"What an amazing turnout.  This was my first year and the attendance has been overwhelming... in a great way.  I had tons of face time with local seniors, which is exactly what I''m looking for."  Jason Resto, Osborn Health & Rehabilitation.\r\n\r\n"Thank you all for a great event!  There were so many seniors who "weathered the weather" to attend the expo and we really didn''t expect such a great turnout.  We received a ton of great contacts and hope to be invited back to next year''s expo.  I cannot imagine what your staff went through to rearrange the table placment and move the entire event inside, but all of the exhibitors received great traffic flow.  Awesome job!"  Renee Wittrock, Wittrock Financial, Inc.\r\n \r\n"The "All Things Senior" Expo was the best tradeshow I''ve ever participated in.  I received more follow-up calls from direct customer contacts I made at this expo than many others combined."  Alex Quintana, Aerocare Air Ambulance\r\n\r\n"This was the best expo for Scottsdale''s senior community.  There were hundreds of resources available to enhance seniors'' lives.  We received a tremendous benefit from having a booth there.  Thanks for a terrific event!"  Liz Ufnal, Santé of North Scottsdale', '"All Things Senior" Expo & Tradeshow', 'If you are looking for information about healthcare, senior housing, municipal services, recreation, technology, transportation or entertainment, the "All Things Senior" Expo & Tradeshow will provide lasting connections to help enhance your quality of life.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'all-things-senior-expo-tradeshow', '', '', '2014-11-20 19:49:34', '2014-11-20 19:49:34', '', 0, 'http://dev.mcdowellvillage.com/?post_type=tribe_events&#038;p=735', 0, 'tribe_events', '', 0),
