(762, 8, '2014-11-21 00:23:27', '2014-11-21 00:23:27', '<h3>Be spoiled. You''ve earned it.</h3>\r\nWhat should you expect from a community that offers world-class senior care service? Why world-class senior care services of course!\r\n\r\nFrom your weekly housekeeper to the front desk attendant just a phone call away, we are standing by. You''ll be surrounded with people who not only love what they do, but love to serve others. Enjoy inspired meals from our chefs or a custom fitness plan from a personal trainer. Our travel concierge awaits your day, weekend or tropical getaway requests. And we''re always available to book your manicure, pedicure or massage. Or all three.\r\n\r\nTake a look at the full list of WESTclass services in Scottsdale. Because you deserve to be spoiled.', 'Services & Amenities', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '256-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-11-21 00:23:27', '2014-11-21 00:23:27', '', 256, 'http://dev.mcdowellvillage.com/blog/256-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(764, 8, '2014-11-21 00:33:38', '2014-11-21 00:33:38', '<h3>Be artistic. Be a green thumb. Be rhumba-ed. Belong.</h3>\r\nWhat makes a community a community? The people, of course. Not to mention the barbecues, rhumba lessons, movie nights, "friendly" card games, gardening sessions, art classes, evening discussions and neighborly support.\r\n\r\nWith so many daily and weekly activities to choose from, you''re bound to make friends and learn interesting things. Your new community is waiting. Join us.\r\n\r\nThe following is only a partial list of what we offer:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Pool and Hot Tub</li>\r\n	<li>Movie Nights in the Theatre</li>\r\n	<li>Computer Lab and Library</li>\r\n	<li>Happy Hours and Other Social Events</li>\r\n	<li>Billiard Room</li>\r\n	<li>Outdoor Patios</li>\r\n	<li>Weekly Games Schedule</li>\r\n	<li>Arts &amp; Crafts</li>\r\n	<li>Barbecues</li>\r\n	<li>Yoga and Tai Chi</li>\r\n	<li>Guest Lectures and Seminars</li>\r\n	<li>Trips to Local Restaurants, Shopping, and Cultural Events</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Community Activities', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '268-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-11-21 00:33:38', '2014-11-21 00:33:38', '', 268, 'http://dev.mcdowellvillage.com/blog/268-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
