(781, 8, '2014-11-21 00:58:46', '2014-11-21 00:58:46', '<h3>Be coiffed.  Be pampered.  Be spoiled.</h3>\r\nWho needs a day of indulgence? You do. Fortunately, Scottsdale''s finest salon and spa services are just a hot stone''s throw from your front door.\r\n\r\nOur salon and spa menu includes:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Haircut and styling</li>\r\n	<li>Manicure</li>\r\n	<li>Pedicure</li>\r\n	<li>Rejuvenating facials</li>\r\n	<li>A full range of massage options, including a sumptuous hot stone massage</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nEnjoy.', 'Salon', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '280-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-11-21 00:58:46', '2014-11-21 00:58:46', '', 280, 'http://dev.mcdowellvillage.com/blog/280-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(782, 8, '2014-11-21 01:00:01', '2014-11-21 01:00:01', '<h3>To know you is to know your favorite kind of smoothie.</h3>\nYour physical, intellectual, emotional and spiritual well-being is important to us. That''s why we get to know you as a person. Your likes. Your dislikes. Your hobbies. Even your favorite special recipe or classic movie. In fact, you''ll swear we read your mind as we offer up events, activities and treats tailor-made for you. Crave a morning smoothie? Check. Like to work out mid-day? No problem. Looking forward to a relaxing massage at the end of your day? Yeah, we thought so.\n\n<strong>Wellness Benefits Include:</strong>\n<ul>\n	<li>Daily Exercise and Fitness Programs</li>\n	<li>Strengthening and Balance</li>\n	<li>Yoga</li>\n	<li>Arthritis Foundation Exercise Classes</li>\n	<li>Walking Groups</li>\n	<li>Equipped Exercise Room</li>\n	<li>Social and Intellectual Stimulation</li>\n	<li>Educational Seminars</li>\n	<li>Religious Worship</li>\n	<li>Intergenerational Programs</li>\n	<li>Music, Dance, Entertainment and Art</li>\n	<li>Brain Fitness Games</li>\n	<li>Stimulating Activities</li>\n</ul>\n<strong>Health and Well-Being Benefits Include:</strong>\n<ul>\n	<li>Comprehensive Health Assessment</li>\n	<li>Pharmacy Consultation Services</li>\n	<li>Medication Oversight</li>\n	<li>Physical, Occupational Therapy</li>\n	<li>Fall Management Program</li>\n	<li>Healthy Dining Choices</li>\n	<li>Massage and Spa Treatment</li>\n</ul>\nLearn more about <a href="http://www.mcdowellvillage.com/senior_living/living_options/assisted_living.html">assisted living in Scottsdale</a>.', 'Senior Wellness', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '286-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-11-21 01:00:01', '2014-11-21 01:00:01', '', 286, 'http://dev.mcdowellvillage.com/blog/286-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
